Name: Name Puzzle, Easter Gift for Boy, Baby's First, First Birthday Gift for Boy, New Baby, Wooden Toys, Custom Name Puzzle, Basket Stuffer
Description:
Our personalized name puzzles make the perfect gift for first birthday's, baby showers, Easter, or any occasion!

A gift you love giving, our wooden name puzzles are a wonderful learning toy to give for birthdays, special occasions and "Just because I Love You"!

• FREE Shipping!
• Personalized gift shows you care
• Fun and educational
• Stand available separately, see link below
• Handmade in Upstate, NY

COLORS: This puzzle includes Olive Green, Light Sage Green, and Ochre Yellow

Puzzles are a fun learning toy that encourage name recognition, spelling, and fine motor skills. They are time tested and never go out of style. Made of high quality baltic birch, our puzzles are 4.5" tall and the length varies based on the length of the name. The puzzles typically range from 10" long, to a maximum length of 23" based on the number of letters and shapes. The letters are approximately 3" high, the perfect size to grab for your young learner. All of the puzzle pieces are raised, making it easy to get them out and play with. We use a combination of non-toxic paint, eco friendly ink, and a food grade non-toxic wood sealer that is child friendly on our puzzles.

The exact colors used and order of the colors will vary from puzzle to puzzle. The number of colors used varies based on the number of letters in a name. Due to differences in monitors and devices, the colors may appear slightly different than shown on your screen. If you have a specific request, please leave it in the Notes to Seller and we are happy to accommodate you if we can. We are not able to include special characters like hyphens or apostrophes in our puzzles. Our puzzles only include uppercase letters, without any special characters.

SENDING AS A GIFT: We offer gift wrap, and can enclose a gift message for you. Please choose the gift wrap or gift note selections at checkout. We do not send a packing slip with price on any of our orders, as many orders are sent directly to the recipient as a gift.

PUZZLE STAND:
To add a puzzle display stand, please use this listing. You can add both items to your cart and checkout at once to receive free shipping on the stand!
https://www.etsy.com/listing/815194794

FREE SHIPPING: We offer FREE 2 Day Shipping on most orders via UPS 3 Day Air. In select locations that we are unable to ship UPS, such as PO Boxes, Hawaii, and Alaska, as well as rural locations without UPS delivery, we ship via USPS Priority Mail.

RETURNS: We do not accept returns on customized items. However, if you have any questions or concerns with your order, please don't hesitate to reach out. Our number one goal is that you LOVE your order! If we make a mistake, we will always make it right for you.

CANCELLATIONS: We work hard to start work on your order as soon as possible! Due to our quick processing time and the personalized nature of this product, we are currently unable to accept cancellations after the order is placed. If you have any questions, please feel free to reach out before placing your order. Thank you!

Description:
· Name Puzzle with Shapes and Numbers ·

★Dimensions
-Puzzle Board (Big Board) : 42x27,5 cm (16,5x10,82 inches)
-Average Letter, Shapes and Numbers Height  : 6-8 cm (2,36 - 3,14 inches) 

★100% Guarantee
We pack it very well to avoid any damage to the product during the shipping phase. However, in case of any damage or problem, it is under our 100% guarantee. If the product is damaged during shipping, we will send a new one immediately.

★Shipping	
-Order processing time: 3-5 business days
-Shipping time: Canada, USA: Maximum 3 business days
			                     Europe: 1-2 business days
				             Japan, Australia, New Zealand: 4-8 business days
★Thoughtfully Made
As an original American brand, our puzzles, which are handcrafted from the most natural woods in our special workshop in Anatolia, are eco-friendly, unique, high quality and fully customizable. It is light, durable and robust. Our carefully prepared personalized puzzle boards and shapes are very smooth. As a result of our trials and research in Europe and America, we have combined the best experiences, bringing together the most exciting shapes and the most popular color variations.

•	Cheerful and Bright Colors
•	Extra Special with Engraving Message
•	Perfect Size
•	Very Quick Shipping
•	Handmade/Only 2 Ingredients: High Quality Natural Anatolian Wood and Water Based Paint
•	100% Safe and Secure
•	100% Guaranteed for any damaged issues during shipping

★Discovering the World
•	Supports kid’s motor skills
•	Teaches balance and coordination 
•	Nurtures kid’s creativity, imagination, problem solving and sharing skills
•	Gets familiar with the basics of daily usage shapes
•	Recognizes name and developing spell 
•	Discovers potentials and world
•	Increases kid’s curiosity 
•	Much more better instead of focusing to a digital screen 

★High Safety – Greenguard Certificate
When producing our high quality puzzles, safety is a high priority for us, as well as design and instruction. For this reason, puzzle corners are oval, not pointed. The pieces on the puzzle do not have sharp or any surface that will harm your child. We're also the only store on Etsy that uses water-based, non-toxic, Greenguard-certified paints.
	 
★A Great Educational Toy, Super Cute Gift Option 
By taking Puzzle, one of the oldest known educational and entertaining games, to a different dimension with its incredibly beautiful, tried-and-tested colors and shapes, we have created puzzles that will be a perfect educational-busy board toy, a super sweet gift, and a perfect decoration and keepsake.

★Safe Usage Instructions and Fragrance
· Try not to leave children under 0-36 months alone with puzzles. Thin and long items such as the letter "I" (if you have them in your puzzle) can be dangerous for children. They may try to swallow.
· Our puzzles may have a wood burning smell when they first reach you. This scent usually lasts up to 1 week. It does not have any harmful or allergenic properties.
· When you receive your puzzle, it is recommended to gently wipe the side black parts of the board and the side black parts of the pieces with a very slightly damp cloth or squeezing a little cologne (without wetting the cloth too much). Please do not wipe the upper parts (painted parts) of the parts.
!!! Important Note: Our puzzles do not have any of the allergenic fragrances specified in the European Union Toy Safety Directive and Legislation.
· The wood we use in our puzzles does not have the risk of becoming bedridden like birch plywood.
· A very small amount of natural glue is used for gluing the puzzle board plates (special Israeli glue with the lowest chemical properties). Since it is used between the bottom and top plate (in only puzzle's board), there is no possibility for the child to come into contact with it. It has no connection with the outside of the puzzle in any way. For this reason, the child can safely take it into his mouth and bite.

★Zuzu Puzzle
Zuzu Puzzle brand is growing rapidly. It's now on Etsy and very new on here. Brings its amazing puzzles to more kids and babies. Zuzu Puzzle cares about the experiences and ideas of its customers. You can contact us 24/7 for any idea, experience or problem. (The average turnaround time for Zuzu Puzzle is a maximum of 8 hours.)

Name: Baby Girl Name Puzzle, Personalized Puzzle With Farm Animals, 3 Years Old, Christmas Gifts For Kids, Wooden Toddler Toys, Montessori Board
Description:
Personalized Name Puzzle With Animals from BusyPuzzle is the Best Wooden Gift for Kids

· COUPON ·
When buying 2 or more Baby Toys or Christmas Decor, we have an additional coupon discount: BUSYPUZZLE
Just add it to your shopping cart.

Our puzzle is based on all that you need. It will let you spend time with your child, will help him to develop his motor skills. Besides, we added an option to engrave Your unique message for your child. You both will enjoy it!

Baby is exploring the world with this game! He learns about what wood looks like and smells like, you can also show him colors. Of course, the baby will easily remember his name because children adore games, it is the best way to teach them. Furthermore, there are animals, so you can tell your baby about them, where do they live, what do they eat, etc. It is so important for the baby to learn the world around him, to know what the dog or cat is saying. And it will be more joyful if you will do it together!

It is the best way to show him how much you love him because for children it is important to be and play with their mom.

· Facilities Of Puzzles ·

- baby's own name
- different animals
- colors
- materials
- shapes and details

All these things your child can learn from just one Puzzle game! Show your baby how much you love him, present him with a special lovely puzzle.

· About Our Puzzles ·

It is made from wood and water-ink, so it is completely eco-friendly and safe for children and the environment.
It is easy to use and the perfect details’ size lets your baby take it comfy. We chose optimal width and this size got the highest mark from you. It perfectly fits your baby (we highly recommend it for 1+ babies).
Our puzzle was inspired by the Montessori technique. The simple technique of making a puzzle will let you do your own stuff while your baby is playing. But don't forget that you can spend time together and have fun.

· Actual Dimensions ·

PLEASE NOTE, that the size of board and animals was changed in order to keep same price.

Height:
4 animals: 5.9 inches (15.5 cm)
8 animals: 9 inches (23 cm)
*The length of the board depends of number of letters.

· Customization ·

Only in this puzzle, you can choose between 5 options (please, choose all the animals from the photo in the listing)
- name puzzle
- name puzzle with 1 animal
- name puzzle with 2 animals
- name with 4 animals
- name with 8 animals
You can also choose the base color (see infographic).

· You can choose one of the animal sets presented in the infographics. Also create your own puzzle by choosing the color of the name and variations of the animals.
· Choose the base of the puzzle. White base can be added at additional cost.
· You can add a unique engravement if you want.
· Gift Wrap is also important so we added options for you to choose from so you can order a real gift, not just a puzzle.
· And finally, we offer a puzzle stand so you can admire it every day.


· Have Any Questions ? ·

• If you got a damaged product - contact us. We are ready to return your full price for bad quality.
• Remember, that we don’t own delivery services and can’t control this process. So, if you have trouble with the time of shipping - check if your product was sent correctly. If all were sent in time - the problem is from the part of the delivery service.
• If your dog ate the shape of the puzzle or you lost it - we are ready to send you a new set of letters for a good price.


· Terms And Conditions For Safe Use ·

1. All kids have imagination. And we made all we can to give you a safe toy. But be careful and try not to leave your child alone with puzzles. Instead - play with your kid. Collect memories
2. Ensure that the child does not take small parts for him.
3. IF IN YOUR PUZZLE YOU HAVE LETTER ”I” - BE ATTENTIVE. THIS SHAPES CAN BE DANGEROUS FOR KIDS 0-3. DON’T LEAVE YOUR CHILD ALONE. OR WE CAN MAKE SHAPES BE FIXED TO THE PUZZLE.

Description:
The main goal of our shop EcoBabyPuzzle is to create natural and non-toxic toys for kids. We can proudly say that we create quality toys that are not only bright and fun but also educational.

This wooden world map puzzle will help your kids understand the wide world around them better! Your little one will develop problem-solving skills, and learn how things fit together. Bight pieces of the puzzle will encourage them to learn colors and differentiate shapes. The world map puzzle shows all continents and their countries, as well as the oceans, which can be the most interesting geography lesson ever for your child!

SIZE:
Length: 16.53" (42cm)
Width: 11.80" (30cm)

OPTIONS:
Puzzle only
Puzzle with a stand
Puzzle with linen bag

DETAILS:
Entirely handmade
Made of natural materials
Bright colors
Made using safe, non-toxic paint
Perfect educational toy for 3-5 year olds
Great for working on fine motor skills

Name Puzzle With Animals, Personalized Gift For Kids, Baby Boy Birthday Gift, First Christmas Gift, Woodland Animals, Montessori Wooden Toys
Description:
Personalized Name Puzzle With Animals from BusyPuzzle is the Best Wooden Gift for Kids

· COUPON ·
When buying 2 or more Baby Toys or Christmas Decor, we have an additional coupon discount: BUSYPUZZLE
Just add it to your shopping cart.

Our puzzle is based on all that you need. It will let you spend time with your child, will help him to develop his motor skills. Besides, we added an option to engrave Your unique message for your child. You both will enjoy it!

Baby is exploring the world with this game! He learns about what wood looks like and smells like, you can also show him colors. Of course, the baby will easily remember his name because children adore games, it is the best way to teach them. Furthermore, there are animals, so you can tell your baby about them, where do they live, what do they eat, etc. It is so important for the baby to learn the world around him, to know what the dog or cat is saying. And it will be more joyful if you will do it together!

It is the best way to show him how much you love him because for children it is important to be and play with their mom.

· Facilities Of Puzzles ·

- baby's own name
- different animals
- colors
- materials
- shapes and details

All these things your child can learn from just one Puzzle game! Show your baby how much you love him, present him with a special lovely puzzle.

· About Our Puzzles ·

It is made from wood and water-ink, so it is completely eco-friendly and safe for children and the environment.
It is easy to use and the perfect details’ size lets your baby take it comfy. We chose optimal width and this size got the highest mark from you. It perfectly fits your baby (we highly recommend it for 1+ babies).
Our puzzle was inspired by the Montessori technique. The simple technique of making a puzzle will let you do your own stuff while your baby is playing. But don't forget that you can spend time together and have fun.

· Actual Dimensions ·

PLEASE NOTE, that the size of board and animals was changed in order to keep same price.

Height:
4 animals: 5.9 inches (15.5 cm)
8 animals: 9 inches (23 cm)
*The length of the board depends of number of letters.

· Customization ·

Only in this puzzle, you can choose between 5 options (please, choose all the animals from the photo in the listing)
- name puzzle
- name puzzle with 1 animal
- name puzzle with 2 animals
- name with 4 animals
- name with 8 animals
You can also choose the base color (see infographic).

· You can choose one of the animal sets presented in the infographics. Also create your own puzzle by choosing the color of the name and variations of the animals.
· Choose the base of the puzzle. White base can be added at additional cost.
· You can add a unique engravement if you want.
· Gift Wrap is also important so we added options for you to choose from so you can order a real gift, not just a puzzle.
· And finally, we offer a puzzle stand so you can admire it every day.


· Have Any Questions ? ·

• If you got a damaged product - contact us. We are ready to return your full price for bad quality.
• Remember, that we don’t own delivery services and can’t control this process. So, if you have trouble with the time of shipping - check if your product was sent correctly. If all were sent in time - the problem is from the part of the delivery service.
• If your dog ate the shape of the puzzle or you lost it - we are ready to send you a new set of letters for a good price.


· Terms And Conditions For Safe Use ·

1. All kids have imagination. And we made all we can to give you a safe toy. But be careful and try not to leave your child alone with puzzles. Instead - play with your kid. Collect memories
2. Ensure that the child does not take small parts for him.
3. IF IN YOUR PUZZLE YOU HAVE LETTER ”I” - BE ATTENTIVE. THIS SHAPES CAN BE DANGEROUS FOR KIDS 0-3. DON’T LEAVE YOUR CHILD ALONE. OR WE CAN MAKE SHAPES BE FIXED TO THE PUZZLE.

Description:
· Math Name Puzzle ·

The fact is, any puzzle can provide benefits, and it’s best to start small children with simple puzzles so they can learn what to do, without becoming frustrated. As they master easy puzzles, they can begin trying more difficult ones, with more pieces and complex designs.

· COUPON ·
When buying 2 or more Baby Toys or Christmas Decor, we have an additional coupon discount: BUSYPUZZLE
Just add it to your shopping cart.

Toddlerhood is a time for curiosity, exploration and learning—all tenants of the Montessori method, a child-centered approach to education. If you’ve found Montessori to be a good fit for your little one and your family, then focusing on toys that support this philosophy can be the perfect way to encourage your little one’s learning through play.

· Possibilities Of The Math Name Puzzle ·

Kids of all ages can gain benefits from playing with puzzles. These brain-building activities help develop cognitive and fine-motor skills, foster cooperative play and spur problem-solving prowess. Not only are puzzles a perfect way to spend some quality time together, but kids feel proud of themselves for completing one. Better yet, they’re an interactive way to teach colors, letters, numbers, shapes, animals and beyond.

When your child tries to put together a puzzle, they are only going to succeed when they find the proper place for each, individual piece. The actual act of manipulating each piece, testing and turning it to see if it fits, is how children learn essential problem solving and critical thinking skills.

· About Our Puzzles ·

- Made with birch plywood and water-based ink, our puzzles are absolutely eco-friendly and safe for kids.
- We have found an ideal size, now there are light, lasting, and easily usable.
- The technique of playing with a name puzzle is inspired by the Montessori technique. Our puzzle can give your child possibilities to learn without your involvement. But still - use every time to form friendships with your kids.

· Customization ·

- You can add pegs to letters and shapes.
- You have 10 different color schemes. Choose every you like. 
PLEASE NOTE, if you didn’t specify the style of the selected Puzzle in the personalization box, then we’ll send you the style of the Puzzle as on the main photo of the listing.
- You can add to your puzzle the back engraving to make it even more personal.
- Choose gift wrap to make your puzzle be a real gift.
- Additionally, we offer you a puzzle stand, so your toy will be a beautiful element of nursery decor.

· Dimensions ·

16.5x16.9 inches (42.2X43.3 cm)
Approximate weight 675 gram.

· Have Any Questions? ·

• If you got a damaged product - contact us. We are ready to return your full price for bad quality.
• Remember, that we don’t own delivery services and can’t control this process. So, if you have trouble with the time of shipping - check if your product was sent correctly. If all were sent in time - the problem is from the part of the delivery service.
• If your dog ate the shape of the puzzle or you lost it - we are ready to send you a new set of letters for a good price.

· Terms And Conditions For Safe Use ·

1. All kids have imagination. And we made all we can to give you a safe toy. But be careful and try not to leave your child alone with puzzles. Instead - play with your kid. Collect memories
2. Ensure that the child does not take small parts for him.
3. IF IN YOUR PUZZLE YOU HAVE LETTER ”I” OR NUMBER “1” - BE ATTENTIVE. THIS SHAPES CAN BE DANGEROUS FOR KIDS 0-3. DON’T LEAVE YOUR CHILD ALONE. OR WE CAN MAKE SHAPES BE FIXED TO THE PUZZLE.

Name: Name Puzzle With Animals, Christmas Gifts, Toys 2 Years Old, Busy Puzzle With Pegs at Extra Charge, Montessori Board, Woodland Animals Toys
Description:
Personalized Name Puzzle With Animals from BusyPuzzle is the Best Wooden Gift for Kids

· COUPON ·
When buying 2 or more Baby Toys or Christmas Decor, we have an additional coupon discount: BUSYPUZZLE
Just add it to your shopping cart.

Our puzzle is based on all that you need. It will let you spend time with your child, will help him to develop his motor skills. Besides, we added an option to engrave Your unique message for your child. You both will enjoy it!

Baby is exploring the world with this game! He learns about what wood looks like and smells like, you can also show him colors. Of course, the baby will easily remember his name because children adore games, it is the best way to teach them. Furthermore, there are animals, so you can tell your baby about them, where do they live, what do they eat, etc. It is so important for the baby to learn the world around him, to know what the dog or cat is saying. And it will be more joyful if you will do it together!

It is the best way to show him how much you love him because for children it is important to be and play with their mom.

· Facilities Of Puzzles ·

- baby's own name
- different animals
- colors
- materials
- shapes and details

All these things your child can learn from just one Puzzle game! Show your baby how much you love him, present him with a special lovely puzzle.

· About Our Puzzles ·

It is made from wood and water-ink, so it is completely eco-friendly and safe for children and the environment.
It is easy to use and the perfect details’ size lets your baby take it comfy. We chose optimal width and this size got the highest mark from you. It perfectly fits your baby (we highly recommend it for 1+ babies).
Our puzzle was inspired by the Montessori technique. The simple technique of making a puzzle will let you do your own stuff while your baby is playing. But don't forget that you can spend time together and have fun.

· Actual Dimensions ·

PLEASE NOTE, that the size of board and animals was changed in order to keep same price.

Height:
4 animals: 5.9 inches (15.5 cm)
8 animals: 9 inches (23 cm)
*The length of the board depends of number of letters.

· Customization ·

Only in this puzzle, you can choose between 5 options (please, choose all the animals from the photo in the listing)
- name puzzle
- name puzzle with 1 animal
- name puzzle with 2 animals
- name with 4 animals
- name with 8 animals
You can also choose the base color (see infographic).

· You can choose one of the animal sets presented in the infographics. Also create your own puzzle by choosing the color of the name and variations of the animals.
· Choose the base of the puzzle. White base can be added at additional cost.
· You can add a unique engravement if you want.
· Gift Wrap is also important so we added options for you to choose from so you can order a real gift, not just a puzzle.
· And finally, we offer a puzzle stand so you can admire it every day.


· Have Any Questions ? ·

• If you got a damaged product - contact us. We are ready to return your full price for bad quality.
• Remember, that we don’t own delivery services and can’t control this process. So, if you have trouble with the time of shipping - check if your product was sent correctly. If all were sent in time - the problem is from the part of the delivery service.
• If your dog ate the shape of the puzzle or you lost it - we are ready to send you a new set of letters for a good price.


· Terms And Conditions For Safe Use ·

1. All kids have imagination. And we made all we can to give you a safe toy. But be careful and try not to leave your child alone with puzzles. Instead - play with your kid. Collect memories
2. Ensure that the child does not take small parts for him.
3. IF IN YOUR PUZZLE YOU HAVE LETTER ”I” - BE ATTENTIVE. THIS SHAPES CAN BE DANGEROUS FOR KIDS 0-3. DON’T LEAVE YOUR CHILD ALONE. OR WE CAN MAKE SHAPES BE FIXED TO THE PUZZLE.

Montessori children's knife and cutting board, handmade. Made by Carpathian wool
Description:
#Falls you like: I am happy to give you a 10% discount - just write me directly to here or under: Knuephi@gmail.com.
Imagine: You cook in the kitchen and your children are very proud that they can help cut fruit, cheese or cooked vegetables. Would be great wouldn't it? But... would you give these cute lemmings sharp knives in your hand? I never in life.

That's why we produce the Cutti and the Boardi!

Both elements are purely handmade! All corners of the boards, after they have been milled out, are individually polished by hand so that everything is nice and soft and flatters the hands. The "knives" are manually tapered for sharpness and edges are smoothed to give a comfortable hold in a small hand. The last step is rubbing with a mixture of beeswax and linseed oil. The product is natural, contains no chemical elements and smells pleasantly of wood.

Sharp things are (sometimes) boys' thing. Exclusively for Carpathian wool, Oleg & Oleg Jr. make the Cutti & Boardi for your kids. Oleg has a wife and a small baby named Anyuta. Oleg knows almost everything about wood, the forest and the mountains. Oleg Jr. Is a student, but what a student! He studies at the Institute of Decorative and Applied Arts at the Faculty of Woodworking near Kossiv.

Some facts:

A) We only use oak wood.
B) Sustainable tree felling is central to us.
C) Weight of Cutti & Boardi: about 1kg.
D) For the treatment of the wood we use pure flaxseed oil.
E) Production takes place in small village communities in the Northeastern Carpathians.
F) We avoid any intermediaries and ensure fair payment of the producers.

Name: Wooden cats family puzzle Nursery baby decor Family keepsake gifts Mother's day gift animal family wooden toys animals kids animal figurines
Description:
The family of animal figures is a unique, meaningful, eco-friendly and long-lasting gift for any occasion, whether it's an anniversary, birthday, new year or to tell of a new addition to the family.

Size:
height - 13,5 cm
width - 15,5 cm
thickness - 2-2,3 cm

The figurines are made of natural wood (oak, ash, birch) entirely by hand, from sketching to coating.

The figurines are coated with edible linseed oil, which has anaesthetic, wound-healing and disinfecting properties. Babies can not only play with these toys but also chew them, it is safe and good for their teeth. Playing with wooden toys, a baby can touch and feel natural materials and improve tactile sensations and fine motor skills.
 
Packaging: simple cardboard boxes, ideal for shipping. We pack all items in kraft wrapping paper (recyclable), tie with twine and affix a "handmade with love" sticker.
 
Cleaning method: clean the product gently, using only a clean damp cloth.  Please do not use disinfectants, hot water or submerge the toy under water.  You can then coat with linseed oil.

This product is handmade and may differ slightly in texture and wood tone from what you see in the photos, you are getting a unique piece!

Description:
· Puzzle with Name and Animals ·

★A Great Educational Toy, Super Cute Gift Option 
By taking Puzzle, one of the oldest known educational and entertaining games, to a different dimension with its incredibly beautiful, tried-and-tested colors and shapes, we have created puzzles that will be a perfect educational-busy board toy, a super sweet gift, and a perfect decoration and keepsake.

★Dimensions
-Puzzle Size with 8 Animals		          : 42x27,5cm (16,5x10,82 inches)
-Average Letter and Animal Height            : 6-8 cm (2,36 - 3,14 inches)

Info About Pegs! : As being a shop which is sensitive for babies health, we strictly avoid using pegs in our puzzle since they may be dangerous as being swallowed or choking hazard. Puzzle pieces are higher than the board.

★Shipping 
Be sure that your puzzle will come to you very well wrapped and packaged. And we use the fastest shipping. Work with DHL and FEDEX.
-Order processing time: 3-5 business days (maximum)
-Shipping time: 
· USA, Canada: 3 business days (maximum) 
· Europe: 1-2 business days (maximum) 
· Japan, Australia, New Zealand: 4-8 business days

★Thoughtfully Made
As an original American brand, our puzzles, which are handcrafted from the most natural woods in our special workshop in TX and Anatolia, are eco-friendly, unique, high quality and fully customizable. It is light, durable and robust. Our carefully prepared personalized puzzle boards and shapes are very smooth. As a result of our trials and research in Europe and America, we have combined the best experiences, bringing together the most exciting shapes and the most popular color variations.

★ Benefits Of This Puzzle
· Supports kid’s motor skills
· Teaches balance and coordination 
· Supports spatial intelligence development
· Increases ability to focus
· Self-confidence: Increases self-confidence
· Problem solving ability: Gains practicality in producing solutions
· Eliminates attention deficit
· Improves visual memory
· Happiness: The child playing with the puzzle enjoys it and becomes happy
· Gets familiar with the basics of daily usage shapes
· Recognizes name and developing spell 
· Discovers potentials and world
· Increases kid’s curiosity 
· Much more better instead of focusing to a digital screen 

★High Safety – Greenguard Certificate
When producing our high quality puzzles, safety is a high priority for us, as well as design and instruction. For this reason, puzzle corners are oval, not pointed. The pieces on the puzzle do not have sharp or any surface that will harm your child. We're also the only store on Etsy that uses water-based, non-toxic, Greenguard-certified paints.

★Guarantee
Unless there is a situation caused by you, such as typing the delivery address incorrectly, in all other conditions, all errors and damages are completely under our %100 guarantee. One of the most common problems with orders is wrongly written addresses. Please check carefully when writing your address.

· We pack the puzzles very well to avoid any damage to the product during the shipping phase. However, If there is damage in the shipping process or an mistake for any reason, we will definitely send a new puzzle as fast as possible without extra charge.

· We have production centers in both Texas and Turkey. We deliver our EU orders from Turkey and our US and Canadian orders from our warehouse in TX. We can also send US orders from Turkey during peak order periods such as Christmas. But don't worry about it at all because it doesn't affect order delivery times in any way. Our delivery time is the same for both our products from Texas and from Turkey. It is exactly the same process from the materials we use for the products to the regulations. Thank you for your understanding.

★Safe Usage Instructions and Fragrance
· Try not to leave children under 0-36 months alone with puzzles. Thin and long items such as the letter "I" (if you have them in your puzzle) can be dangerous for children. They may try to swallow.
· Our puzzles may have a wood burning smell when they first reach you. This scent usually lasts up to 1 week. It does not have any harmful or allergenic properties.
· When you receive your puzzle, it is recommended to gently wipe the side black parts of the board and the side black parts of the pieces with a very slightly damp cloth or squeezing a little cologne (without wetting the cloth too much). Please do not wipe the upper parts (painted parts) of the parts.
!!! Important Note: Our puzzles do not have any of the allergenic fragrances specified in the European Union Toy Safety Directive and Legislation.
· The wood we use in our puzzles does not have the risk of becoming bedridden like birch plywood.
· A very small amount of natural glue is used for gluing the puzzle board plates (special Israeli glue with the lowest chemical properties). Since it is used between the bottom and top plate (in only puzzle's board), there is no possibility for the child to come into contact with it. It has no connection with the outside of the puzzle in any way. For this reason, the child can safely take it into his mouth and bite.

★Zuzu Puzzle
Zuzu Puzzle brand is growing rapidly. It's now on Etsy and very new on here. Brings its amazing puzzles to more kids and babies. Zuzu Puzzle cares about the experiences and ideas of its customers. You can contact us 24/7 for any idea, experience or problem. (The average turnaround time for Zuzu Puzzle is a maximum of 8 hours.)

Name: Animal Theme Baby Name Puzzle, Personalized Montessori Board, Christmas Gifts For Kids, 2 Yers Old Gift, Stacking Stuffer Toy, Wooden Toys
Description:
Personalized Name Puzzle With Animals from BusyPuzzle is the Best Wooden Gift for Kids

· COUPON ·
When buying 2 or more Baby Toys or Christmas Decor, we have an additional coupon discount: BUSYPUZZLE
Just add it to your shopping cart.

Our puzzle is based on all that you need. It will let you spend time with your child, will help him to develop his motor skills. Besides, we added an option to engrave Your unique message for your child. You both will enjoy it!

Baby is exploring the world with this game! He learns about what wood looks like and smells like, you can also show him colors. Of course, the baby will easily remember his name because children adore games, it is the best way to teach them. Furthermore, there are animals, so you can tell your baby about them, where do they live, what do they eat, etc. It is so important for the baby to learn the world around him, to know what the dog or cat is saying. And it will be more joyful if you will do it together!

It is the best way to show him how much you love him because for children it is important to be and play with their mom.

· Facilities Of Puzzles ·

- baby's own name
- different animals
- colors
- materials
- shapes and details

All these things your child can learn from just one Puzzle game! Show your baby how much you love him, present him with a special lovely puzzle.

· About Our Puzzles ·

It is made from wood and water-ink, so it is completely eco-friendly and safe for children and the environment.
It is easy to use and the perfect details’ size lets your baby take it comfy. We chose optimal width and this size got the highest mark from you. It perfectly fits your baby (we highly recommend it for 1+ babies).
Our puzzle was inspired by the Montessori technique. The simple technique of making a puzzle will let you do your own stuff while your baby is playing. But don't forget that you can spend time together and have fun.

· Actual Dimensions ·

PLEASE NOTE, that the size of board and animals was changed in order to keep same price.

Height:
4 animals: 5.9 inches (15.5 cm)
8 animals: 9 inches (23 cm)
*The length of the board depends of number of letters.

· Customization ·

Only in this puzzle, you can choose between 5 options (please, choose all the animals from the photo in the listing)
- name puzzle
- name puzzle with 1 animal
- name puzzle with 2 animals
- name with 4 animals
- name with 8 animals
You can also choose the base color (see infographic).

· You can choose one of the animal sets presented in the infographics. Also create your own puzzle by choosing the color of the name and variations of the animals.
· Choose the base of the puzzle. White base can be added at additional cost.
· You can add a unique engravement if you want.
· Gift Wrap is also important so we added options for you to choose from so you can order a real gift, not just a puzzle.
· And finally, we offer a puzzle stand so you can admire it every day.


· Have Any Questions ? ·

• If you got a damaged product - contact us. We are ready to return your full price for bad quality.
• Remember, that we don’t own delivery services and can’t control this process. So, if you have trouble with the time of shipping - check if your product was sent correctly. If all were sent in time - the problem is from the part of the delivery service.
• If your dog ate the shape of the puzzle or you lost it - we are ready to send you a new set of letters for a good price.


· Terms And Conditions For Safe Use ·

1. All kids have imagination. And we made all we can to give you a safe toy. But be careful and try not to leave your child alone with puzzles. Instead - play with your kid. Collect memories
2. Ensure that the child does not take small parts for him.
3. IF IN YOUR PUZZLE YOU HAVE LETTER ”I” - BE ATTENTIVE. THIS SHAPES CAN BE DANGEROUS FOR KIDS 0-3. DON’T LEAVE YOUR CHILD ALONE. OR WE CAN MAKE SHAPES BE FIXED TO THE PUZZLE.

Description:
Looking for Personalized Baby Name Puzzle with Pegs, First Christmas Gift idea or any other day of the year? Here it's - the pastel name puzzle is a simple and nice toy for kids that helps them develop motor skills, starting to speak and compose their first own words with their parents.

GET MORE.

Occasion ideas: 
🎄 Christmas gift for kids
🎁 1st Birthday Gift, Second or Third Birthday Gift
🌿Wood - Eco friendly Toy
🌻 Nursery Decor
🧸Baby Shower Gift
📸Baby Photo Prop
🎉Newborn Gift

About our Puzzles:
🤎 Our wooden sorters are made out of highest quality grade birch plywood and letters are laser cut with every corner carefully rounded and the y are absolutely eco - friendly and safe for kids.
🤎 Size - their length varies from 8 to 24 inches (depending from the baby name and extra options) so they are light, lasting and easily usable.
Each board is 0.31 inches thin (8mm)
Each letter is 0.31 inches thin (8mm) and 2.36 inches tall (6cm)
🤎 The technique of playing with our baby name puzzles are inspired by the Montessori technique.

Personalization:
We are gladly make a unique and lovely puzzle for your kids , so you can personalized it:
- Custom color scheme for letters 
- Add additional elements to puzzle (like: animals, space theme, cars, figures)
- Add wishing engraving on the back.

FAQ 
1) What the "Pegs" are?
It's a small rounded part on letters and elements that helped baby easily hold the elements.
2) What does it means - "additional elements"?
You can add to puzzle with baby name extra figure that will be on the beginning of puzzle or on the beginning and in the end (if you choose 2 extra elements) - it's great idea for personalized you gift.
3) Is it possible to get a preview of puzzle with my Personalization?
Yes, please contact us and we will send a mockup with your custom information.

Description:
Personalized Name Puzzle With Animals from BusyPuzzle is the Best Wooden Gift for Kids

· COUPON ·
When buying 2 or more Baby Toys or Christmas Decor, we have an additional coupon discount: BUSYPUZZLE
Just add it to your shopping cart.

Our puzzle is based on all that you need. It will let you spend time with your child, will help him to develop his motor skills. Besides, we added an option to engrave Your unique message for your child. You both will enjoy it!

Baby is exploring the world with this game! He learns about what wood looks like and smells like, you can also show him colors. Of course, the baby will easily remember his name because children adore games, it is the best way to teach them. Furthermore, there are animals, so you can tell your baby about them, where do they live, what do they eat, etc. It is so important for the baby to learn the world around him, to know what the dog or cat is saying. And it will be more joyful if you will do it together!

It is the best way to show him how much you love him because for children it is important to be and play with their mom.

· Facilities Of Puzzles ·

- baby's own name
- different animals
- colors
- materials
- shapes and details

All these things your child can learn from just one Puzzle game! Show your baby how much you love him, present him with a special lovely puzzle.

· About Our Puzzles ·

It is made from wood and water-ink, so it is completely eco-friendly and safe for children and the environment.
It is easy to use and the perfect details’ size lets your baby take it comfy. We chose optimal width and this size got the highest mark from you. It perfectly fits your baby (we highly recommend it for 1+ babies).
Our puzzle was inspired by the Montessori technique. The simple technique of making a puzzle will let you do your own stuff while your baby is playing. But don't forget that you can spend time together and have fun.

· Actual Dimensions ·

PLEASE NOTE, that the size of board and animals was changed in order to keep same price.

Height:
4 animals: 5.9 inches (15.5 cm)
8 animals: 9 inches (23 cm)
*The length of the board depends of number of letters.

· Customization ·

Only in this puzzle, you can choose between 5 options (please, choose all the animals from the photo in the listing)
- name puzzle
- name puzzle with 1 animal
- name puzzle with 2 animals
- name with 4 animals
- name with 8 animals
You can also choose the base color (see infographic).

· You can choose one of the animal sets presented in the infographics. Also create your own puzzle by choosing the color of the name and variations of the animals.
· Choose the base of the puzzle. White base can be added at additional cost.
· You can add a unique engravement if you want.
· Gift Wrap is also important so we added options for you to choose from so you can order a real gift, not just a puzzle.
· And finally, we offer a puzzle stand so you can admire it every day.


· Have Any Questions ? ·

• If you got a damaged product - contact us. We are ready to return your full price for bad quality.
• Remember, that we don’t own delivery services and can’t control this process. So, if you have trouble with the time of shipping - check if your product was sent correctly. If all were sent in time - the problem is from the part of the delivery service.
• If your dog ate the shape of the puzzle or you lost it - we are ready to send you a new set of letters for a good price.


· Terms And Conditions For Safe Use ·

1. All kids have imagination. And we made all we can to give you a safe toy. But be careful and try not to leave your child alone with puzzles. Instead - play with your kid. Collect memories
2. Ensure that the child does not take small parts for him.
3. IF IN YOUR PUZZLE YOU HAVE LETTER ”I” - BE ATTENTIVE. THIS SHAPES CAN BE DANGEROUS FOR KIDS 0-3. DON’T LEAVE YOUR CHILD ALONE. OR WE CAN MAKE SHAPES BE FIXED TO THE PUZZLE.

Description:
Caterpillar Theme Wooden Name Puzzle

Our wooden name puzzles are such a fun gift for the little one in your life. Watching them explore and learn is such a joy. So, why not give them a gift that encourages both? ❤

PRODUCT DETAILS
❤ Materials: wooden plywood, non-toxic paint and UV resistant ink
❤ Proudly made with love in the USA
❤ Contains small parts that babies should not be allowed to chew on
❤ Puzzle size: 11 inches wide, 10 inches tall (13 inches tall for double name)
❤ Letters measure approximately 2.5 inches tall
❤ Puzzle pieces are raised so they are easy to lift out of frame
❤ Personalized message can be engraved on back of puzzle
❤ Puzzle stand can be added to your order

We offer options for single name (example: Wyatt) and double name (example: Stetson Wyatt), options to add a personalized engraved message on the back, and options to add a stand that allows the design to be displayed upright. You can choose from these options in the listing's drop-down menu. 😘

This puzzle was created for P L A Y, but please do not leave children unattended with this wooden design. Instead, play with them! You'll treasure the memories that are made. ❤

Montessori Busy Board, Personalized Puzzle Name, Toy Gifts for Baby, Custom Name Puzzle for Toddlers, Custom Wooden Puzzle, Baby Shower Gift

Our custom puzzle board is both durable and environmentally friendly. The busy board is not only a toy for entertainment but also a montessori toy for children's fundamental development, such as identity colors, shapes, animal species, spelling their names, etc. The wooden puzzle board is the perfect gift for children aged 1 to 10 who are always hungry to learn. It can be a birthday present, a holiday gift for your kids and your friend's kids, or even a memorial keepsake as well. Children, on the other hand, should be aware of the letter "I," which may be a little easy to swallow, and parents should play with them.

Description:
· Puzzle with Name and Animals ·

★A Great Educational Toy, Super Cute Gift Option 
By taking Puzzle, one of the oldest known educational and entertaining games, to a different dimension with its incredibly beautiful, tried-and-tested colors and shapes, we have created puzzles that will be a perfect educational-busy board toy, a super sweet gift, and a perfect decoration and keepsake.

★Dimensions
-Puzzle Size with 4 Animals		          : 42x20cm (16,5x8,00 inches)
-Puzzle Size with 8 Animals		          : 42x27,5cm (16,5x10,82 inches)
-Average Letter and Animal Height            : 6-8 cm (2,36 - 3,14 inches)

Info About Pegs! : As being a shop which is sensitive for babies health, we strictly avoid using pegs in our puzzle since they may be dangerous as being swallowed or choking hazard. Puzzle pieces are higher than the board.

★Shipping 
Be sure that your puzzle will come to you very well wrapped and packaged. And we use the fastest shipping. Work with DHL and FEDEX.
-Order processing time: 3-5 business days (maximum)
-Shipping time: 
· USA, Canada: 3 business days (maximum) 
· Europe: 1-2 business days (maximum) 
· Japan, Australia, New Zealand: 4-8 business days

★Thoughtfully Made
As an original American brand, our puzzles, which are handcrafted from the most natural woods in our special workshop in TX and Anatolia, are eco-friendly, unique, high quality and fully customizable. It is light, durable and robust. Our carefully prepared personalized puzzle boards and shapes are very smooth. As a result of our trials and research in Europe and America, we have combined the best experiences, bringing together the most exciting shapes and the most popular color variations.

★ Benefits Of This Puzzle
· Supports kid’s motor skills
· Teaches balance and coordination 
· Supports spatial intelligence development
· Increases ability to focus
· Self-confidence: Increases self-confidence
· Problem solving ability: Gains practicality in producing solutions
· Eliminates attention deficit
· Improves visual memory
· Happiness: The child playing with the puzzle enjoys it and becomes happy
· Gets familiar with the basics of daily usage shapes
· Recognizes name and developing spell 
· Discovers potentials and world
· Increases kid’s curiosity 
· Much more better instead of focusing to a digital screen 

★High Safety – Greenguard Certificate
When producing our high quality puzzles, safety is a high priority for us, as well as design and instruction. For this reason, puzzle corners are oval, not pointed. The pieces on the puzzle do not have sharp or any surface that will harm your child. We're also the only store on Etsy that uses water-based, non-toxic, Greenguard-certified paints.

★Guarantee
Unless there is a situation caused by you, such as typing the delivery address incorrectly, in all other conditions, all errors and damages are completely under our %100 guarantee. One of the most common problems with orders is wrongly written addresses. Please check carefully when writing your address.

· We pack the puzzles very well to avoid any damage to the product during the shipping phase. However, If there is damage in the shipping process or an mistake for any reason, we will definitely send a new puzzle as fast as possible without extra charge.

· We have production centers in both Texas and Turkey. We deliver our EU orders from Turkey and our US and Canadian orders from our warehouse in TX. We can also send US orders from Turkey during peak order periods such as Christmas. But don't worry about it at all because it doesn't affect order delivery times in any way. Our delivery time is the same for both our products from Texas and from Turkey. It is exactly the same process from the materials we use for the products to the regulations. Thank you for your understanding.

★Safe Usage Instructions and Fragrance
· Try not to leave children under 0-36 months alone with puzzles. Thin and long items such as the letter "I" (if you have them in your puzzle) can be dangerous for children. They may try to swallow.
· Our puzzles may have a wood burning smell when they first reach you. This scent usually lasts up to 1 week. It does not have any harmful or allergenic properties.
· When you receive your puzzle, it is recommended to gently wipe the side black parts of the board and the side black parts of the pieces with a very slightly damp cloth or squeezing a little cologne (without wetting the cloth too much). Please do not wipe the upper parts (painted parts) of the parts.
!!! Important Note: Our puzzles do not have any of the allergenic fragrances specified in the European Union Toy Safety Directive and Legislation.
· The wood we use in our puzzles does not have the risk of becoming bedridden like birch plywood.
· A very small amount of natural glue is used for gluing the puzzle board plates (special Israeli glue with the lowest chemical properties). Since it is used between the bottom and top plate (in only puzzle's board), there is no possibility for the child to come into contact with it. It has no connection with the outside of the puzzle in any way. For this reason, the child can safely take it into his mouth and bite.

★Zuzu Puzzle
Zuzu Puzzle brand is growing rapidly. It's now on Etsy and very new on here. Brings its amazing puzzles to more kids and babies. Zuzu Puzzle cares about the experiences and ideas of its customers. You can contact us 24/7 for any idea, experience or problem. (The average turnaround time for Zuzu Puzzle is a maximum of 8 hours.)

Name: Puzzle Fairy Tale Little Red Riding Hood
Description:
The puzzle fairy tale Little Red Riding Hood by Fragmentis consists of 25 pieces and is suitable for children from 3 years of age.

Here not only a beautiful puzzle is put together, but the motif tells the whole fairy tale. Once the puzzle has been set up, the child can use the pictures to follow the individual stages of the fairy tale. A small Little Red Riding Hood figure is attached, which can hike along while reading the fairy tale. It shows how Little Red Riding Hood first leaves the house, meets the bad wolf while picking flowers, he makes the plan to eat Little Red Riding Hood and the grandmother, how Little Red Riding Hood meets the wolf in the grandmother's bed and how the wolf is finally defeated with the help of the hunter. The text of the fairy tale is enclosed with the puzzle. Later, you can also let the child retell the fairy tale himself.

The puzzle not only trains the concentration and motor skills of the children, but is also intended to help the children to tell a story themselves.

The fairy tales of the Brothers Grimm are part of the German cultural heritage and have been conveyed to our children for generations.

The puzzle is 29 x 17 cm in size. The packaging includes 24 puzzle pieces, a Little Red Riding Hood figure, a linen bag and the assembly instructions with the fairy tale text.

The puzzle is made of 3 mm thick high-density hardboard and printed with colors certified for children. The puzzle is cut with laser and is packed in a box made of 100% recycled cardboard. Sustainability is important to me and plastic is completely dispensed with.

The motif is a separate design by Fragmentis. The puzzle is made according to the European guidelines for toy safety.

Not suitable for children under 3 years of age. Contains small parts - risk of choking!

Description:
Wooden toys are play-ready for ages 6 months. Personalized wooden name puzzles are a particularly timely gift for a baby shower or first birthday! A personalized name puzzle and cute animals, cartoon characters will be playmates for older girls and boys.


1️⃣Type of Wood
We use birch plywood to make a personalized name puzzle

2️⃣Letters
The baby's name puzzle uses capital letters

3️⃣Letter Font
The letter font of the name puzzle created by the illustrator is cute and safe - without sharp corners and sharp edges

4️⃣Letter Size
The letter height 2.68" / 6.8 cm. The letters are of a safe size so that the baby does not swallow them. But the baby will be safe when he plays only under the supervision of adults!

5️⃣Elements
With the help of a UV printing machine and certified water-based paint and varnish, we make puzzle animals especially realistic. The baby will not only see particularly colorful elements, but will feel the rough, wavy, striped surfaces when touching them with his fingers.

6️⃣Colors
“Rainbow” is a popular color scheme for our wooden name puzzles. We offer some sets offer pastel or designer color palettes to pick from.
Color comes down to your preference. Please choose your favorite letters colors from the color palette you can find between the photos.
🟥Colors may look different on your display depending on their settings and technical characteristics. If you are uncertain and the color shade is really important, please contact with us or order samples.

Additional options you can choose to complete your gift.
7️⃣Engraving
Engraving one of wooden toys’ main attractions. Spelling your child’s name with wooden puzzle pieces — an engraving on the back of your puzzle makes it more personalized heirloom item to be cherished for a lifetime.

8️⃣Stand
The stand is perfect for holding a name puzzle board to decorate the baby's room. The stand is decorated with the sun, moon and clouds.
Not suitable for baby play.

9️⃣Personalized Name Puzzle Board sizes is depending on number of letters and Number of Elements selected.

Montessori Busy Board | Personalized Puzzle | Sensory Activity | Wooden Toys | Baby Boy Gift | First Christmas Gift | Unique Birthday Gift
Description:
· Busy Board With Name ·

The philosophy behind toys like the Montessori Busy Boards is quite simple: Real toys. Mostly Wood. Not Too Many.
This is based on the belief that children need to be encouraged to explore the world around them. Play is a huge part of a child’s development.

· About Puzzle ·

Children learn quickly through play by touching and exploring various objects. A busy board is a Montessori Toy that stimulates learning through experiments. It is a toy that a child can touch and hold. Learning to manipulate everyday objects help children develop their fine motor skills. It will also help him figure out and work things out on their own and at their own pace.

You don’t need a lot of toys for your toddler. Less can be more with a curious toddler who loves to tinker. What they love are playing with wooden blocks, jumping on a mini couch, tinkering with a box of plastic kitchen tools, strewing paper across the living room floors, and enjoying an open-ended play. These are all design to develop their gross motor skills and provide an opportunity for toddlers to explore their surroundings. The best way to provide your child with the full sensory experience is to give him a Montessori busy board.

· Facilities Of This Puzzle ·

☆ Montessori toy. They are simple, made of natural materials, and functional. These are the best toys for our little ones’ development that allow them to explore and involve their own will, decisions, and ideas.
☆ Build Nerve Connections in the Brain. The more sensory experiences your child has, the stronger are the pathways that are developed.
☆ Sensory play can be quite calming for kids. Perhaps, you have noticed it – handing something interesting to your baby would help quiet him down.
☆ High quality. We use only first-class safe materials such as wood and non-toxic ink so your child is perfectly safe with this puzzle. Materials are only eco-friendly and safe for humans (water-based ink, wood).

· Customization And Safety ·

☆ You can choose one of the 10 color schemes. If you want to learn with your child colors - choose rainbow. Or if you like the classic style - choose the wooden color scheme.
☆ You can add a stand, which displays the puzzle in your playroom
☆ The backside is where you can place your engraving message. Kids will grow older, new toys will be needed, but your warm wishes will stay forever.
☆ The toy is safe. We use water-based paint, smooth wooden materials to give you assurance. But of course, we ask you to be attentive while your child is playing.

· Dimensions ·

16.1x9 in (41.5x23 cm)
Weight 710 grams.

· Have Any Questions? ·

• If you got a damaged product - contact us. We are ready to return your full price for bad quality.
• Remember, that we don’t own delivery services and can’t control this process. So, if you have trouble with the time of shipping - check if your product was sent correctly. If all were sent in time - the problem is from the part of the delivery service.
• If your dog ate the shape of the puzzle or you lost it - we are ready to send you a new set of letters for a good price.

· Terms And Conditions For Safe Use ·

1. All kids have imagination. And we made all we can to give you a safe toy. But be careful and try not to leave your child alone with puzzles. Instead - play with your kid. Collect memories
2. Ensure that the child does not take small parts for him.
3. IF IN YOUR PUZZLE YOU HAVE LETTER ”I” - BE ATTENTIVE. THIS SHAPES CAN BE DANGEROUS FOR KIDS 0-3. DON’T LEAVE YOUR CHILD ALONE. OR WE CAN MAKE SHAPES BE FIXED TO THE PUZZLE.

Educational Puzzle With Shapes And Numbers, Custom Name Puzzle, Preschool Montessori Toys, Wooden Toddler Toys, Christmas Gifts For Kids
Description:
· Math Name Puzzle ·

The fact is, any puzzle can provide benefits, and it’s best to start small children with simple puzzles so they can learn what to do, without becoming frustrated. As they master easy puzzles, they can begin trying more difficult ones, with more pieces and complex designs.

· COUPON ·
When buying 2 or more Baby Toys or Christmas Decor, we have an additional coupon discount: BUSYPUZZLE
Just add it to your shopping cart.

Toddlerhood is a time for curiosity, exploration and learning—all tenants of the Montessori method, a child-centered approach to education. If you’ve found Montessori to be a good fit for your little one and your family, then focusing on toys that support this philosophy can be the perfect way to encourage your little one’s learning through play.

· Possibilities Of The Math Name Puzzle ·

Kids of all ages can gain benefits from playing with puzzles. These brain-building activities help develop cognitive and fine-motor skills, foster cooperative play and spur problem-solving prowess. Not only are puzzles a perfect way to spend some quality time together, but kids feel proud of themselves for completing one. Better yet, they’re an interactive way to teach colors, letters, numbers, shapes, animals and beyond.

When your child tries to put together a puzzle, they are only going to succeed when they find the proper place for each, individual piece. The actual act of manipulating each piece, testing and turning it to see if it fits, is how children learn essential problem solving and critical thinking skills.

· About Our Puzzles ·

- Made with birch plywood and water-based ink, our puzzles are absolutely eco-friendly and safe for kids.
- We have found an ideal size, now there are light, lasting, and easily usable.
- The technique of playing with a name puzzle is inspired by the Montessori technique. Our puzzle can give your child possibilities to learn without your involvement. But still - use every time to form friendships with your kids.

· Customization ·

- You can add pegs to letters and shapes.
- You have 10 different color schemes. Choose every you like. 
PLEASE NOTE, if you didn’t specify the style of the selected Puzzle in the personalization box, then we’ll send you the style of the Puzzle as on the main photo of the listing.
- You can add to your puzzle the back engraving to make it even more personal.
- Choose gift wrap to make your puzzle be a real gift.
- Additionally, we offer you a puzzle stand, so your toy will be a beautiful element of nursery decor.

· Dimensions ·

16.5x16.9 inches (42.2X43.3 cm)
Approximate weight 675 gram.

· Have Any Questions? ·

• If you got a damaged product - contact us. We are ready to return your full price for bad quality.
• Remember, that we don’t own delivery services and can’t control this process. So, if you have trouble with the time of shipping - check if your product was sent correctly. If all were sent in time - the problem is from the part of the delivery service.
• If your dog ate the shape of the puzzle or you lost it - we are ready to send you a new set of letters for a good price.

· Terms And Conditions For Safe Use ·

1. All kids have imagination. And we made all we can to give you a safe toy. But be careful and try not to leave your child alone with puzzles. Instead - play with your kid. Collect memories
2. Ensure that the child does not take small parts for him.
3. IF IN YOUR PUZZLE YOU HAVE LETTER ”I” OR NUMBER “1” - BE ATTENTIVE. THIS SHAPES CAN BE DANGEROUS FOR KIDS 0-3. DON’T LEAVE YOUR CHILD ALONE. OR WE CAN MAKE SHAPES BE FIXED TO THE PUZZLE.

Made of high quality baltic birch, our puzzles are 4.5" tall and the length varies based on the length of the name. RETURNS: We do not accept returns on customized items. However, if you have any questions or concerns with your order, please don't hesitate to reach out. Our number one goal is that you LOVE your order! If we make a mistake, we will always make it right for you.

CANCELLATIONS: We work hard to start work on your order as soon as possible! Description:
Name Puzzle

Our beautiful wooden Name Puzzles are a fun way to encourage name/letter recognition, spelling, and fine motor skills.  Fun, thoughtful, and educational gift for a baby shower, birthday or Christmas for the little ones in your life!  Unique way to announce your baby's name.  Also, great for nursery or playroom decor!

MATERIALS:
Name puzzles are made of high-quality Baltic Birch and are hand sanded. The cast acrylic letters are raised making the letters easy for little fingers to grab, get out and play with.  Letters and board are rounded with no sharp edges.  We use non-toxic paint and wax sealer that are food safe and child friendly.  The unpainted wood sections are sanded and unfinished.

BONUS WOODEN LETTERS:
Name puzzle comes with an extra set of unfinished wooden letters.  You and your little one can get creative and customize/paint the wooden letters for that extra personalized touch!  Or you can use them as nursery decor!

COLORS PICTURED: H-Hunter Green, U-Greige, D-Mustard, S-Greige, O-Green, N-Greige
***PLEASE NOTE: Your name puzzle will be painted in the exact colors as pictured unless you choose custom colors and list them in the personalization box***
*Colors can vary depending on the screen or computer you are using*

CUSTOM COLOR OPTIONS: 
Hunter Green, Mustard, Green, Blush, Pink, Teal, Navy, Light Blue, Gold, Grey, Greige, Cream, White, Black, or unpainted natural birch wood.
***Please be sure to list your color choices in the order you wish to have them painted***
     EX: OLIVER ---> O-Navy, L-White, I-Grey, V-Navy, E-White, R-Grey. 

Click here to find the matching ABC Board - https://www.etsy.com/listing/1317117938/abc-puzzle-wooden-alphabet-acrylic?ref=listings_manager_grid

FONT STYLE: 
The letters in this puzzle are created using a fun and unique font style that adds a modern flair to your standard block letters.
If you are looking for a puzzle with more block/bold style letters, please check out this name puzzle - https://www.etsy.com/listing/1317576726/name-puzzle-wooden-name-puzzle?ref=listings_manager_grid

SIZE:
Board: Approximately 4" tall without engraving and 4.5" tall with engraving on the front.  Length depends on the number of letters in the name.
Letter Width and Height: 1/4" thick and approximately 2.5" tall

ENGRAVING:
You have the option to add a first name and middle name engraved on the front.  If you would like to do so, please select the engraving option and write out the name. 

Natural wood grain with beautiful color variations throughout making each one unique.  Wood pieces may be slightly different in color or contain natural occurring knots/marks.  No two pieces are identical.  

All products are handcrafted from start to finish here in Southern California.

Description:
Busy Board for toddler with free and Fast Shipping

Please choose your size from drop down menu

Handmade wooden fidget, busy board enhanced with real-life elements. Let your child explore small real-life elements safely. Entirely handmade and hand-painted from child-friendly elements, smoothened and painted with child-safe, non-toxic paint. A sensory toy that belongs in the Montessori toy categories.

Practical, educational, and decorative educational game. Perfect from 10 months up, for toddlers and pre-school kids. The sensory board promotes play-and-learn excitement with locks, latches, buttons, gears, screws, keys, from metal and wood. A busy board that is filled with fun while serving as a creative tool to enhance the child’s learning skills. It is a simple activity that will keep your baby challenged, interested but also has so many different benefits.  A child learns new subjects, forms, and colors, stimulates their mind, help keep their hands busy, while allows your child to solve a problem and to feel the satisfaction of opening, closing, resolving the problem

While the sensory busy board is specially made for toddlers, it makes a perfect match for the elderly as well, perfect for adults with dementia or Alzheimer's, as busy boards support hand control, muscle strength & finger dexterity.

MAIN BENEFITS OF THIS GAME THAT WILL HELP THE CHILD’S DEVELOPMENT
- Improves concentration and memory
- Stimulates learning through experiments
- Develops fine motor skills
- Encourages critical thinking
- Improves matchmaking skills
- Shape recognition
- Goal setting 
- Problem solving
- Teaches patience
- Builds a sense of achievement
- Improves logical thinking
- Explores the finger grip, touching

Buy it for your baby or gift it. Makes a unique gift for any occasion, and once the children no longer play with it you can display it on a shelf or keep it as a forever keepsake. Makes a great gift for baby shower, birthday, baby welcoming, for new parents, Christmas, etc. This is the type of gift that you can pass down from generation to generation.

• Coated with water-based paint that is safe for children

Description:
Nine arch-shaped elements made of the highest quality layered birch wood. It is both a creative toy for children and a design piece for adults.
The rainbow is really versatile: children can build, sort, stack, and as the they grow older, their imagination will open up the endless ways of using it. It can be a bridge, a tunnel, a fence, a house, a pyramid and so much more!  Anything from learning colors to building sculptures! It helps your child develop fine motor skills, tactile experience, attention, concentration, counting skills, patience and imagination. The toy is crafted with the highest care and attention to every detail. All surfaces are especially soft and smooth and because of the layered wood, it will never crack or break.
It includes a wooden ball to create a labyrinth and a mallet to use it as a xylophone (to create different sounds and melodies).

A unique and unforgettable memory that remains for life.

In addition, the personalized wooden puzzle is great as a decoration for the children's room - on the room door or on the wall. It is an educational toy that helps your child develop motor skills and identify shapes. Our puzzles are inspired by Montessori techniques and promote fine motor skills and early self-esteem.

A great gift idea for your loved ones for birth or baptism, for birthdays, Easter or Christmas, for the baby shower party and so on.

Personalization:

The letters themselves are 6 mm thick and about 8 cm high.

Description:
Individual, decorative and instructive at the same time. This personalized puzzle is carved from the right wood. 👌

The puzzle is custom-made for you and consists of a combination of symbols and the child's name. The simple yet loving design and the colorful colors fascinate every toddler and help him to develop the motor skills while playing.

This name wooden puzzle is the ideal GIFT for a birth, the 1st, 2nd or 3rd birthday, baby shower and also a real eye-catcher under the Christmas tree.

material:

The wooden board and the individual letters are cut out of birch plywood, this wood is extremely stable and additionally lighter than most types of wood. The colours are applied with child-friendly acrylic paint based on water (according to DIN EN 71-3).

COLOR THEMES:

The name is designed in different color combinations: PASTELL, RAINBOW 🌈 and CUSTOM (custom). You can simply select the desired version from the 1st options menu. If you choose CUSTOM, please include the appropriate letter combination (A-T) in the text box. For example: "GLGLGL" or "FEGEF".

The colors "S" and "T" are gold and silver respectively

symbols:

In this puzzle, you can also select 1 or 2 symbols.

IMPORTANT: CHOOSE IN THE MENU PLEASE PLEASE 2 BOOKS PRO DESIRED SYMBOL!
For example, if you want to order the name LAURA with 2 symbols, you select --> 5 + 2 + 2 = 9 BOOKS in the menu.

In addition, enter the correct combination of number (1-20) and letter (A-T) in the text box. For example, if you want a blue butterfly and a pink cloud, please enter "7E" and "9H".

The first symbol is to the left of the name. If you select 2 symbols, the 1st is placed on the left and the 2nd to the right of the name.


PERSONAL MESSAGE:

You can select the number of letters of the name in the 2nd menu. If you want to have a PERSONAL MESSAGE engraved on the back of the board, please select "+ GRAVUR" in the 2nd menu. (Max. 100 characters)

The CHILD's NAME, color combinations, symbol combinations, and the (optional) text on the back can be inserted into the text box.

This Montessori wooden toy adorns the baby room and is a LEARNING THAT both children and parents have fun with.

dimensions:

Length: from 40 cm to... (depending on the length of the name)

The letters and symbols are 4 mm higher than the background and are therefore easy to remove.

- baby's own name

- colors
- materials
- shapes and details

All these things your child can learn from just one Puzzle game! Show your baby how much you love him, present him with a special lovely puzzle.

· About Our Puzzles ·

It is made from wood and water-ink, so it is completely eco-friendly and safe for children and the environment.
It is easy to use and the perfect details’ size lets your baby take it comfy. We chose optimal width and this size got the highest mark from you. It perfectly fits your baby (we highly recommend it for 1+ babies).
Our puzzle was inspired by the Montessori technique. The simple technique of making a puzzle will let you do your own stuff while your baby is playing. But don't forget that you can spend time together and have fun.

· Terms And Conditions For Safe Use ·

Description:
Looking for safe wooden toys for your little champ?

Our puzzle with forest animals is a fun learning tool that encourages fine motor skills, name recognition, and spelling. Made of non-toxic birch plywood, our name board contains child-friendly elements (letters) that are easy to get out and play with.

Our name board never goes out of style. So you’re welcome to order this time tested toy to:
★ Get a unique and sweet birthday gift for toddlers.
★ Prepare a baby shower gift to impress a mom-to-be.
★ Provide a kid with a safe toy for an independent game.
★ Give a special present that is not only fun but also strengthens hand-eye coordination and fine motor skills.
★ Get a personalized gift that shows how much you care and makes the kid feel special.
★ Use our woodland nursery decor to add some meaningful design to your kid’s room. Perfectly matches both your room décor and the personality of the little one.
★ Have a universal gift for a baby boy, baby girl, toddlers and kids.

Details: 
★ The size of the board is suitable for a little hand: 30 x 40 cm (11,8 x 15,7 inches).
★ Each name puzzle is 0.31 inches thin (8mm) while every letter is 0.15 inches thin (4mm) and 2.36 inches tall (6cm).
★ Options available: puzzle board and two animals puzzle.
★ We offer 9 different puzzle characters that you can combine however you like.
★ Please, notice that if you choose two shape puzzle and mention only one character you will get puzzle with two identical animals on the sides.
★  You’re welcome to order the boards with the most unusual names – all products are customizable.

Delivery specifications:
All of the name boards are produced in 1-3 business days. If you customize your purchase, the timeframe can differ. Our STANDARD delivery for the USA - 7-10 business days, for the UK- 8-14 business days, for Europe - 8-16 business days, for Canada - 3-6 business days. In the case of the other countries, the standard delivery takes 3-6 business days.

http://eepurl.com/h6inOH

Wooden ABC Puzzle

Welcome our wooden alphabet puzzle of perfect quality and just right size of letters!

Perfect gift for kids 2-5 years old, it is also an adorable nursery decoration.

If you want to buy your kid a useful, developing and interesting toy- you are at the right place. We really don't think there is much to talk about here, this puzzle speaks for itself! Your kid will love putting letters in the cut-outs, meanwhile learning letters, their shapes and places in the Alphabet. 
Mom will have extra time for a cup of coffee and a child will spend some good time playing this thing. You can also spend some quality time together, learning and playing simultaneously.

Here is some more details:

Made from the birch plywood, covered with water-based, eco-friendly paints, which are absolutely sage for children.

If you have ANY questions please contact us <3

Name Puzzle | Wooden Name Puzzle
Description:
Name Puzzle

Our beautiful wooden Name Puzzles are a fun way to encourage name/letter recognition, spelling, and fine motor skills.  Fun, thoughtful, and educational gift for a baby shower, birthday or Christmas for the little ones in your life!  Also, great for nursery or playroom decor!

MATERIALS:
Name puzzles are made of high-quality Baltic Birch and are hand sanded. The cast acrylic letters are raised making the letters easy for little fingers to grab, get out and play with.  Letters and board are rounded with no sharp edges.  We use non-toxic paint and wax sealer that are food safe and child friendly.  The unpainted wood sections are sanded and unfinished.

BONUS WOODEN LETTERS:
Name puzzle comes with an extra set of unfinished wooden letters.  You and your little one can get creative and customize/paint the wooden letters for that extra personalized touch!  Or you can use them as nursery decor!

COLORS PICTURED: I-Blush, N-Mustard, D-Greige, I-Cream, and E-Pink
***PLEASE NOTE: Your name puzzle will be painted in the exact colors as pictured unless you choose custom colors and list them in the personalization box***
*Colors can vary depending on the screen or computer you are using*

CUSTOM COLOR OPTIONS: 
Hunter Green, Mustard, Green, Blush, Pink, Teal, Navy, Light Blue, Gold, Grey, Greige, Cream, White, Black, or unpainted natural birch wood.
***Please be sure to list your color choices in the order you wish to have them painted***
     EX: OLIVER ---> O-Navy, L-White, I-Grey, V-Navy, E-White, R-Grey. 

FONT STYLE: 
The letters in this puzzle are created using an adorable chunky style font with more of a modern block letter.  
If you are interested in a modern font style that adds a modern flair to your standard block letters, please check out this name puzzle - https://www.etsy.com/listing/1330991129/name-puzzle-wooden-name-puzzle?ref=listings_manager_grid

SIZE:
Board: Approximately 4" tall without engraving and 4.5" tall with engraving on the front.  Length depends on the number of letters in the name.
Letter Width and Height: 1/4" thick and approximately 2.5" tall

ENGRAVING:
You have the option to add a first name and middle name engraved on the front.  If you would like to do so, please select the engraving option and write out the name. 

Natural wood grain with beautiful color variations throughout making each one unique.  Wood pieces may be slightly different in color or contain natural occurring knots/marks.  No two pieces are identical.  

All products are handcrafted from start to finish here in Southern California.

⭐- PUZZLE DETAILS

• Size depends of the name length and chosen figure. Height – 3 ¾ inches (3,75 ’’)

• First, Second and Third Birthday Gift

• Baby Shower Gift
• Friend’s Baby Gift

1- Choose the number of letters,
2- Put the desired name , Figure Letters (if you purchased figure), Engraving message (if you purchased Engraving) and color scheme code into the personalization box.
3- Add to cart
4- Check out

Baby Name Puzzle, Busy Board, Woodland Animals, Baby Activity Toy, Toddler Montessori Toys, 2nd Birthday Gift for Daughter, Gift for Kids
Description:
Looking for safe wooden toys for your little champ? Our puzzle with forest animals is a fun learning tool that encourages fine motor skills, name recognition, and spelling. Made of non-toxic birch plywood, our name board contains child-friendly elements (letters) that are easy to get out and play with.

Our name board never goes out of style. So you’re welcome to order this time tested toy to:
★ Get a unique and sweet birthday gift for toddlers.
★ Prepare a baby shower gift to impress a mom-to-be.
★ Provide a kid with a safe toy for an independent game.
★ Give a special present that is not only fun but also strengthens hand-eye coordination and fine motor skills.
★ Get a personalized gift that shows how much you care and makes the kid feel special.
★ Use our woodland nursery decor to add some meaningful design to your kid’s room. Perfectly matches both your room décor and the personality of the little one.
★ Have a universal gift for a baby boy, baby girl, toddlers and kids.

Details: 
★ The size of the board is suitable for a little hand: 30 x 40 cm (11,8 x 15,7 inches).
★ Each name puzzle is 0.31 inches thin (8mm) while every letter is 0.15 inches thin (4mm) and 2.36 inches tall (6cm).
★ Options available: puzzle board and two animals puzzle.
★ We offer 9 different puzzle characters that you can combine however you like.
★ Please, notice that if you choose two shape puzzle and mention only one character you will get puzzle with two identical animals on the sides.
★  You’re welcome to order the boards with the most unusual names – all products are customizable.

Delivery specifications:
All of the name boards are produced in 1-3 business days. If you customize your purchase, the timeframe can differ. Our STANDARD delivery for the USA - 7-10 business days, for the UK- 8-14 business days, for Europe - 8-16 business days, for Canada - 3-6 business days. In the case of the other countries, the standard delivery takes 3-6 business days.
