Baby Girl Gift, Montessori Toys, Personalized Name Puzzle, Kids Birthday Gift Cute Baby 1st Birthday Gift, Baby Shower Gift, Child Wood Toys
Description:
The wooden name puzzle is a fun and effective way to teach your kids letters, colors, shapes, and…their unique names! Puzzle with pegs will save the day for parents looking to both entertain and teach the little ones. Made of non-toxic and durable materials, these Montessori toys are safe for little delicate hands. Besides, we produce each puzzle with smooth edges to ensure our little clients won't get hurt.

We've got loads of styles of baby toys that turn the process of learning letters into a play! Moms and dads are sure to order an item with their child's name on it crafted in eye-friendly colors. Whether you're looking for a personalized gift for the kid's 1st birthday or any other occasion, our portable products are absolutely recommended. 

Please, notice that if you don't mention design in your notes to order - you will get the design is shown on the main photo.  

Order our name puzzles to rock any special occasion!
★Perfect birthday gift for boys and girls to provide quality playtime.
★Cute present for Baby Shower party to make mom's job easier.
★Put our name puzzle under a Christmas tree and admire the little ones opening their presents in an excited mood!
★Order name puzzles to use them as cute nursery decor.
★Our wooden name puzzles are a perfect option to encourage independent play – all ages have fun manipulating each piece, taking it out, testing its durability, and putting it back. If necessary, you’re welcome to join the little one and do the puzzle together!

Details:
★Made out of non-toxic and durable birch plywood.
★Organic and safe materials and paints are used in the production process.
★The shapes on the sides are included in the price.
★GIFT packaging is available at checkout.
★Each name puzzle is a personalized eco-friendly product.
★Each puzzle is 0.31 inches thin (8mm) and each letter is 0.15 inches thin (4mm) and 2.36 inches tall (6cm).

It takes 1-3 business days to craft a wooden name puzzle. Looking for a custom design? We’ll be happy to meet your requirements, but we will need a bit more time to do the job.

Delivery specifications:
Meet our STANDARD delivery rates: 
USA - 7-10 business days; 
United Kingdom - 8-14 business days; 
Europe - 8-16 business days; 
Canada - 3-6 business days. 
Standard delivery to the other counties - 3-6 business days.

Stay updated on the latest and greatest, get special newsletter member discounts and lots of inspiration

It is the best way to show him how much you love him because for children it is important to be and play with their mom.

· Facilities Of Puzzles ·

- baby's own name
- different animals
- colors
- materials
- shapes and details

All these things your child can learn from just one Puzzle game! Show your baby how much you love him, present him with a special lovely puzzle.

· About Our Puzzles ·

It is made from wood and water-ink, so it is completely eco-friendly and safe for children and the environment.
It is easy to use and the perfect details’ size lets your baby take it comfy. We chose optimal width and this size got the highest mark from you. It perfectly fits your baby (we highly recommend it for 1+ babies).
Our puzzle was inspired by the Montessori technique. The simple technique of making a puzzle will let you do your own stuff while your baby is playing. But don't forget that you can spend time together and have fun.

PLEASE NOTE, that the size of board and animals was changed in order to keep same price.

Height:
4 animals: 5.9 inches (15.5 cm)
8 animals: 9 inches (23 cm)

- name puzzle
- name puzzle with 1 animal
- name puzzle with 2 animals
- name with 4 animals
- name with 8 animals
You can also choose the base color (see infographic).

· Choose the base of the puzzle. White base can be added at additional cost.
· You can add a unique engravement if you want.
· Gift Wrap is also important so we added options for you to choose from so you can order a real gift, not just a puzzle.
· And finally, we offer a puzzle stand so you can admire it every day.


· Have Any Questions ? ·

• If you got a damaged product - contact us. We are ready to return your full price for bad quality.
• Remember, that we don’t own delivery services and can’t control this process. So, if you have trouble with the time of shipping - check if your product was sent correctly. If all were sent in time - the problem is from the part of the delivery service.
• If your dog ate the shape of the puzzle or you lost it - we are ready to send you a new set of letters for a good price.


· Terms And Conditions For Safe Use ·

1. All kids have imagination. And we made all we can to give you a safe toy. But be careful and try not to leave your child alone with puzzles. Instead - play with your kid. Collect memories
2. Ensure that the child does not take small parts for him.
3. IF IN YOUR PUZZLE YOU HAVE LETTER ”I” - BE ATTENTIVE. THIS SHAPES CAN BE DANGEROUS FOR KIDS 0-3. DON’T LEAVE YOUR CHILD ALONE. OR WE CAN MAKE SHAPES BE FIXED TO THE PUZZLE.

Wooden Name Puzzle, Custom Name Puzzle, Heirloom Quality Natural Hardwoods, Solid Wood Name puzzle, Personalized name puzzle
Description:
Name puzzles are expertly crafted with bases from solid maple hardwood with an even light tone and smooth grains, that is sanded to a satin finish. Deep nesting pockets are created to cradle the thick, chunky letters. Letters can be selected from any of the four solid hardwoods we offer; maple, hickory, cherry or walnut. These beautiful, heirloom-quality personalized puzzles will grow with your child as they learn through play. 

Name puzzles are a classic gift for any occasion.

Specifications
Puzzles will be crafted in UPPERCASE only.
Available in a 3/4" solid maple hardwood base. Base is 4" tall and the length of base will vary per name.
Letters are approximately 3" in height and 3/4" thick. Wood type choices for letters include solid maple, hickory, cherry or walnut
No stain is used, leaving the natural beauty of the tree itself
If selecting personalized inscriptions, it will go on the back of the base in the right hand corner
We would love to see your child playing with their toys! If you would like to share photos with us, you can tag us on Instagram @timberwooddesigns or email us at hello@timberwooddesigns.ca. 

Disclosure: All wooden toys are crafted in solid natural hardwood. Since wood is natural grains and colours may differ from images shown and scripts may have variations such as light or dark coloured areas, knots and other inconsistencies. This item is not intended as a toy. It is for photo props and decor use. Therefore child should not play with it and always have adult supervision. 

By placing your order, you have acknowledged that we are not responsible for how you use our products and that they may contain variations that are present in all natural hardwoods.  Once the products have left our hands, the purchaser accepts full responsibility & liability for all Timberwood Designs products.

How to Wash
We recommend spot cleaning by hand with warm water and a mild soap. Do not soak in water. Please follow manufacturer's instructions on how to use their products. Timberwood Designs is not responsible for how these products are handled.

Shipping & Returns
Please see our Shipping Policy for current turn around time and a full list of our shipping rates.

Most orders will be shipped via Canada Post or UPS. Shipping times do not include processing time. Delivery time is 4-10 days, signature is required for all UPS deliveries.

Returns & Exchanges

Please see our Refund Policy. 

Cancelling or Modifying Orders

Every piece we create is made custom and to order, therefor all sales are final. In some cases a modification request can be made by email to hello@timberwooddesigns.ca. We pride ourselves on our ability to create and ship orders as quickly as possible, but as a result it may not be possible to modify your order.

Colourful Wood Elephant Puzzle for Kids, Baby puzzle, Animal Puzzle Toy for Toddlers, Wooden Toy for baby
Description:
Here at LithuaniaDESIGN we care about quality, sustainability and healthy lifestyle!

Colourful and cute elephants come to life in this handcrafted 7 piece wooden puzzle for toddlers. Take it apart and play with them individually or learn how to put them back together. Light weight wooden puzzle pieces have a great grip which make them ideal for the little ones. Develop your motor skills, understanding different shapes and sizes, improve your patience and have fun playing!

We care what kind of toys children play with, therefore:

- Our wooden toys are made from locally sourced high quality birch wood - its environmentally friendly, long lasting & biodegradable;
- Chunky natural wood parts help develop sensory skills and stimulate healthy cognitive development;
- Toys are plastic & BPA free;
- Suitable for creative play - no flashing or loud sounds, simple toys that come alive with a little help of limitless kids imagination.

And did we mention that the materials comply with the requirements set by European Union for production of children's toys too? Because of course they do!

Some additional useful information:

Measurements: Tallest elephant hight: 6 cm x 4,3 cm
Suggested age: +3

Note: Actual product might slightly vary from the photo as each toy is handmade and the shades of wood differ piece by piece.

Packaging:

- All products are carefully packaged, too reach you as safe as possible.
- Sending it as a present? Great! Let us know and we will ship the product to an address of your choice, gift wrap it and include any message to give it that loving personal touch.

Shipping:

- Normally it takes 1-2 weeks to Europe, up to 2-4 weeks elsewhere.

Note: Due to Covid-19 pandemic post offices are experiencing delays with shipping. Please keep in mind that your orders might take longer to arrive than estimated. We still continue to process majority of the orders in 1 business day. If you wish that we send your order with tracking, please inform us and we can arrange it for you.

Name: Personalized Sprocket Name Puzzle Acrylic and Wooden Toy Display | BusyWorx©
Description:
We are excited to be exclusively partnered with local maker, Sharks With Laser Beams!

SWLB is a American grown design team based right outside Saint Petersburg, Florida. We are proud to present their latest creation, the coolest kid’s toy you’ve seen in awhile: BusyWorx©

𝙋𝙍𝙊𝘿𝙐𝘾𝙏 𝘿𝙀𝙏𝘼𝙄𝙇𝙎

Help your toddler get a head start developing fine motor skills, shape and color recognition, and even learning their alphabet and spelling. Parents also love displaying BusyWorx on a shelf as imaginative and unique kid’s room display sign décor.

Each piece is made by our own team here in Florida from wood and acrylic. The letters are about 3.5in tall and 2in wide. The sprockets are about 2.5in in diameter.

The letters fit snugly in each sprocket for a very satisfying assembly experience. Spin one letter and they all go rotate in unison!

𝙃𝙊𝙒 𝙏𝙊 𝙊𝙍𝘿𝙀𝙍

Spell out the name or word you’d want in capital letters (Example: “JENNIFER”)

Specify which letter color you want, or you can pick a color theme. If you select a color theme please note that the colors will be randomized for each letter.

If you want one of our shapes included just specify which one. Each shape counts as a letter, so if you specify “JACK, with a Shark Shape” that counts as 5 letters.

Also double check you’ve got the right number of letters when checking out. If you check out with 3 letters but specify “RYAN” as the name, we’ll have to cancel your order and you’ll need to re-check out again with the right number of letters. That’s not fun, so just be careful to avoid that.

𝙎𝙃𝙄𝙋𝙋𝙄𝙉𝙂

Usually ships in about 1-2 business days. Free Standard Shipping on US orders. Shipping upgrades are available upon checkout.


𝙍𝙀𝙁𝙐𝙉𝘿𝙎 𝘼𝙉𝘿 𝙀𝙓𝘾𝙃𝘼𝙉𝙂𝙀𝙎

All items in our shop are made per order and just for you. Personalized pieces are not eligible for refunds or returns.

If there is a material defect with the piece, we will gladly make you a new one. If you have a question or concern about your order, please message us first so we can help fix the situation. We stand behind our work and aim to create the highest quality products.

Please review our shop policy before placing your order for questions concerning proofs, our engraving process, non-personalized returns, international shipping, and delayed/lost packages.
___________

Not intended for kids under 3 years old. Your tot should not be left unattended when playing.

Please note Sharks With Laser Beams has copyrighted and patented their creation and registered it with the US government. Patent Pending.

Wooden Safari Name Puzzle for Toddler - Montessori Toy - Nursery Decor - Wood Name Puzzle - Baby Name Sign - 1st Birthday - Christmas Gifts
Description:
Personalized Name Puzzle With Animals from BusyPuzzle is the Best Wooden Gift for Kids

· COUPON ·
When buying 2 or more Baby Toys or Christmas Decor, we have an additional coupon discount: BUSYPUZZLE
Just add it to your shopping cart.

Our puzzle is based on all that you need. It will let you spend time with your child, will help him to develop his motor skills. Besides, we added an option to engrave Your unique message for your child. You both will enjoy it!

Baby is exploring the world with this game! He learns about what wood looks like and smells like, you can also show him colors. Of course, the baby will easily remember his name because children adore games, it is the best way to teach them. Furthermore, there are animals, so you can tell your baby about them, where do they live, what do they eat, etc. It is so important for the baby to learn the world around him, to know what the dog or cat is saying. And it will be more joyful if you will do it together!

It is the best way to show him how much you love him because for children it is important to be and play with their mom.

· Facilities Of Puzzles ·

- baby's own name
- different animals
- colors
- materials
- shapes and details

All these things your child can learn from just one Puzzle game! Show your baby how much you love him, present him with a special lovely puzzle.

· About Our Puzzles ·

It is made from wood and water-ink, so it is completely eco-friendly and safe for children and the environment.
It is easy to use and the perfect details’ size lets your baby take it comfy. We chose optimal width and this size got the highest mark from you. It perfectly fits your baby (we highly recommend it for 1+ babies).
Our puzzle was inspired by the Montessori technique. The simple technique of making a puzzle will let you do your own stuff while your baby is playing. But don't forget that you can spend time together and have fun.

· Actual Dimensions ·

PLEASE NOTE, that the size of board and animals was changed in order to keep same price.

Height:
4 animals: 5.9 inches (15.5 cm)
8 animals: 9 inches (23 cm)
*The length of the board depends of number of letters.

· Customization ·

Only in this puzzle, you can choose between 5 options (please, choose all the animals from the photo in the listing)
- name puzzle
- name puzzle with 1 animal
- name puzzle with 2 animals
- name with 4 animals
- name with 8 animals
You can also choose the base color (see infographic).

· You can choose one of the animal sets presented in the infographics. Also create your own puzzle by choosing the color of the name and variations of the animals.
· Choose the base of the puzzle. White base can be added at additional cost.
· You can add a unique engravement if you want.
· Gift Wrap is also important so we added options for you to choose from so you can order a real gift, not just a puzzle.
· And finally, we offer a puzzle stand so you can admire it every day.


· Have Any Questions ? ·

• If you got a damaged product - contact us. We are ready to return your full price for bad quality.
• Remember, that we don’t own delivery services and can’t control this process. So, if you have trouble with the time of shipping - check if your product was sent correctly. If all were sent in time - the problem is from the part of the delivery service.
• If your dog ate the shape of the puzzle or you lost it - we are ready to send you a new set of letters for a good price.


· Terms And Conditions For Safe Use ·

1. All kids have imagination. And we made all we can to give you a safe toy. But be careful and try not to leave your child alone with puzzles. Instead - play with your kid. Collect memories
2. Ensure that the child does not take small parts for him.
3. IF IN YOUR PUZZLE YOU HAVE LETTER ”I” - BE ATTENTIVE. THIS SHAPES CAN BE DANGEROUS FOR KIDS 0-3. DON’T LEAVE YOUR CHILD ALONE. OR WE CAN MAKE SHAPES BE FIXED TO THE PUZZLE.

Description:
Tractor Themed Wooden Name Puzzle

Our wooden name puzzles are such a fun gift for the little one in your life. Watching them explore and learn is such a joy. So, why not give them a gift that encourages both? ❤

PRODUCT DETAILS
❤ Materials: wooden plywood, non-toxic paint and UV resistant ink
❤ Proudly made with love in the USA
❤ Contains small parts that babies should not be allowed to chew on
❤ Width (measurement from left to right) varies based on the letters in each name
❤ Height is 3.5 inches for single name and 7 inches for double name
❤ Letters measure approximately 2.5 inches tall
❤ Puzzle pieces are raised so they are easy to lift out of frame
❤ Personalized message can be engraved on back of puzzle
❤ Puzzle stand can be added to your order

This puzzle was created for P L A Y, but please do not leave children unattended with this wooden design. Instead, play with them! You'll treasure the memories that are made. ❤

Thank you for visiting The Puzzled Peacock!

Description:
Looking for the perfect gift that’s cute and educational all in one? 

Look no further! 

Our wooden name puzzles are hand made with laser cut birch wood, safe acrylic paint, cute trendy fabric and sealed with organic Bees Wax and Orange Peel Oil! 

All puzzles are have a width of 3.5 inches and a length of about 6-15 inches depending on the length of the name. All puzzle pieces (letters) are 2.5 inches tall.

With FREE SHIPPING and a FREE ENGRAVING of your choice!   

** Please make sure to add the exact name you would like the puzzle to be as well as the exact wording for engraving on the back In the “personalization box” **

Unfortunately, we do not except returns on personalized items. If a puzzle arrives to you broken or incorrect just shoot us a message and we will get that figured out ASAP!

Baby Boy Gift, Educational Toys for Toddlers, Name Puzzle, Woodland Nursery, Personalized Baby Gifts, Kids Name Puzzle 2nd 3rd Birthday Gift
Description:
Looking for safe wooden toys for your little champ? Our puzzle with forest animals is a fun learning tool that encourages fine motor skills, name recognition, and spelling. Made of non-toxic birch plywood, our name board contains child-friendly elements (letters) that are easy to get out and play with.

Our name board never goes out of style. So you’re welcome to order this time tested toy to:
★ Get a unique and sweet birthday gift for toddlers.
★ Prepare a baby shower gift to impress a mom-to-be.
★ Provide a kid with a safe toy for an independent game.
★ Give a special present that is not only fun but also strengthens hand-eye coordination and fine motor skills.
★ Get a personalized gift that shows how much you care and makes the kid feel special.
★ Use our woodland nursery decor to add some meaningful design to your kid’s room. Perfectly matches both your room décor and the personality of the little one.
★ Have a universal gift for a baby boy, baby girl, toddlers and kids.

Details: 
★ The size of the board is suitable for a little hand: 30 x 40 cm (11,8 x 15,7 inches).
★ Each name puzzle is 0.31 inches thin (8mm) while every letter is 0.15 inches thin (4mm) and 2.36 inches tall (6cm).
★ Options available: puzzle board and two animals puzzle.
★ We offer 9 different puzzle characters that you can combine however you like.
★ Please, notice that if you choose two shape puzzle and mention only one character you will get puzzle with two identical animals on the sides.
★  You’re welcome to order the boards with the most unusual names – all products are customizable.

Delivery specifications:
All of the name boards are produced in 1-3 business days. If you customize your purchase, the timeframe can differ. Our STANDARD delivery for the USA - 7-10 business days, for the UK- 8-14 business days, for Europe - 8-16 business days, for Canada - 3-6 business days. In the case of the other countries, the standard delivery takes 3-6 business days.

Stay updated on the latest and greatest, get special newsletter member  discounts and lots of inspiration
http://eepurl.com/h6inOH

Name: Build Your Own Personalized Alphabet Letters Train. Large 3 inch Each Custom Wooden Baby Name Letter, Wagon and Engine Included, Train Gifts
Description:
Educational Toy For Kids

LEARN, PLAY & DISPLAY.  REMEMBER WE INCLUDE FRONT TRAIN & REAR WAGON AT NO EXTRA CHARGE. 

Encourages logic, fine motor skills, letter recognition, name spelling, self esteem.

Handmade Personalized Large TRAIN Letters For Boys & Girls. 
All letters are capital and they are 3" high. Front Train & Wagon cars are about 3" high and  they are painted with a NONE Toxic water based paint.   


DISCLAIMER: Trains magnets are screwed in and secured with two types of glue. Train Wheels are secured using two types of glue. While we try do everything to guarantee wheels and magnets stay in place they can come off during play. Please use common sense and monitor young children during play just like with any toy that has small parts. All toys with small parts are a chocking hazard. 

Train & Wagon Included - Unusual names & spellings are no problem since these are completely customizable.

Our colors are available in Bright Primary Colors or Muted Pastels. We can make your name train in any color combination just request it under notes to seller. 

Primary colors are assorted in a mix of Red, orange, yellow, green, blue, indigo, or violet.  The engine and wagon are either black or red.  

Pastel colors are assorted in a mixed color combination of Purple, Pink, Yellow, Light Blue, Mint, Peach. The engine and wagon are available in white and yellow. 

Mint and Navy color combination is assorted in a Mint Blue and Navy Color scheme with a grey engine and wagon. 

Boho color combination is assorted in Purple, Pink, Bright Blue, Mint Blue repetition with a white engine and wagon. 

Please choose correct letter count when ordering. For example the name Luke will be 4 letter count. Do not include the engine and wagon in the letter count. 

MADE IN THE USA.

You may also like:
Car Wooden Name Puzzle: https://etsy.me/38Yzp42

Thank you for visiting my shop!

Be sure to check back with my store to see new items!

I appreciate you supporting my small business!

Box of Montessori Mobile, Gobbi Mobile, Munari Mobile, Montessori Ball, Dancer Mobile, Octahedron Mobile, Rattle, Grasping Beads, Crib Toy
Description:
Box of Montessori Mobile,  Gobbi Mobile, Munari Mobile, Dancer Mobile, Octahedron, Mobile Bebe, Red Montessori Ball, Baby Rattle Set, Grasping Beads

You can choose your puzzle ball in a separable or non-separable fixed style.

MOBILE HOLDERS

Wall Mounted 

The product is completely made of hornbeam wood. 
The lenght of mobile holder is 40 cm 15,7". You have to drill the wall and insert the screw that comes out of the set.

Crib Mounted

The product is completely made of hornbeam wood. 
It consists of 3 interlocking parts. You don't need to use any glue as the pieces fit tightly. However, if you are going to hang mobiles over 200 grams, it would be better to stick them with glue. 
To attach it to the cradle, the connector is turned clockwise until it tightens. The total height after attaching the mobile holder to the bassinet is 68 cm & 26.7 inches.

Please click the link below for more detailed pictures.

https://www.etsy.com/listing/1189268286/baby-mobile-holder-crib-mount-mobile?ref=listings_manager_grid

Baby Gym 

The product is completely made of linden wood. 
Installation is completed with two wooden screws. 
The height of the baby gym is 80 cm & 31.5 inches, and the width is 85 cm & 33.5 inches.

Please click the link below for more detailed pictures.

https://www.etsy.com/listing/1203087173/wooden-montessori-baby-gym-mobile-holder?ref=listings_manager_grid

DIMENSIONS OF MOBILES

Octahedron Mobile 

Wooden stick is 30 cm & 11.8"
Each octahedron is 6.5 cm & 2.55"
The red and blue octahedron is 21 cm & 8.26" below the wooden stick. The yellow one is 18 cm & 7.08"

Munari Mobile 

3 wooden sticks - 30/25/15 cm & 11.8"/9.85"/5.9"
The plastic ball is 6 cm & 2.36"
Total length from right to left is approximately 50 cm & 20". Total approximate height from top to bottom is 45 cm & 18"

Gobbi Mobile 

Wooden stick is 30 cm & 11.8"
Each ball is 6 cm & 2.36"

Dancer Mobile 

3 wooden sticks - 30/15/15 cm & 11.8"/5.9"/5.9"
One dancer is 20-25 cm & 8"-10" lenght and 10-15 cm & 4"-6" width
Total length from right to left is approximately 50 cm & 20". Total approximate height from top to bottom is 45 cm & 16"

Rainbow mobile 

Total lenght from right to left approximately 25 cm& 10". Total approximate height from top to bottom is 45 cm & 18"

The lenght of mobile holder is 38,5 cm & 15"

The diameter of puzzle ball is approximately is 12 cm & 4,7".

The Munari is the first of the Montessori Mobiles and it can be used when the baby is a few weeks old.Newborns can only see black, white and shades of gray and they love high contrast images since they can more easily distinguish them.That is why Munari mobile consists of contrasting colors, geometric shapes and a sphere that reflects light.

The Octahedron mobile is the second mobile in the Montessori visual mobile series and it can be used when the baby is a 5-8 weeks old.One month after birth, the baby begins to distinguish high-contrast primary colors. Red is the best visible color for baby. That's why mobile consists of red, yellow and blue color.

The Gobbi mobile is the third in the Montessori visual mobile series. It is used when the baby 7-10 weeks old.The Gobbi mobile consists of 5 balls with a diameter of 6 cm. There are different shades of a color in 5 balls and the baby starts to distinguish color transitions when he/she is 2 months old. Balls are then hung at a 45 degree angle, with the darkest color hung the lowest and the lightest color in the highest position. The baby first sees the dark ball that is closest to him/her. As his/her vision improves, he/she begins to see and distinguish other balls.

The Montessori Dancers Mobile is the 4th mobile in the Visual Mobile Series. It is traditionally offered to a baby around 10-12 weeks of age after the Gobbi Mobile, to help the baby continue developing his/her concentration, dynamic visual focus and depth perception.But the most important thing is to follow your child's own interests and path.Dancer mobile consists of 4 dancing human figures. Since halographic paper is used, light is reflected as the mobile moves, thanks to the wind created by the baby's hand movements.

Rainbow mobile is the 5th mobile. 

The black and white baby rattle is made in sizes that your baby can hold. Thanks to its black and white color, the baby can see it easily. It also makes a sound as it shakes in the baby's hand.The round grip ring helps baby notice the grabbing motion. It contributes to the development of sensory and fine motor skills. It can also be used as a teether.

Montessori ball is designed for children to develop their cognitive and motor skills. Thanks to the shape of the ball, the baby can easily grasp it. It can transfer from one hand to the other. Develops baby's hand and ankle movements. It also helps develop hand-eye coordination.Approximately 13 cm (5,1 inches) in diameter.

Grasping beads is made using 5 wooden spheres. They are in sizes that the baby can easily grasp.

The mobiles should be hung at an eye distance of 20-30 cm, where the baby cannot touch but can see clearly.

The mobiles are already assembled. All you have to do is tie the product's threads to the place you want.

It is recommended to use under adult supervision.
Tags: Montessori Ball,Grasping ring,Set of Montessori,Mobtessori Baby Toys,Montessori Ball,Grasping ring,Set of Montessori,Mobtessori Baby Toys

Name: 12pcs Wooden Montessori Rainbow Stacker Toys, Large Waldorf Rainbow Wooden Puzzle, Educational Learning Toys, Nursery, Christmas Baby Gift
Description:
🌈 Montessori Wooden Toys are open-ended, simple, inspired by nature and designed to promote learning through imaginative, fantasy play. This 
      large 12 pcs wooden rainbow stacker is a perfect birthday gift for toddlers.

🌈 Made of high quality natural solid wood. Provide a non-toxic and safe rainbow stacking game with smooth edges and surfaces for kids. No 
      smell. Perfect for little hands. All of the paints used in our product are harmless to health and EN 71-3 certified. Sanding processes are carried 
      out in our products, there are no sharp edges. 

🌈 We love wood because it is a natural material so it always has various markings that show up in our products, making each one unique. The 
     unique variations are proof of quality, not defects. The stacking block set is handcrafted from natural wood; it may show slight differences 
     (colour differences, knot marks, etc.) from the image. Wood is aesthetically beautiful: it tells the story of nature and life. It is able to be recycled 
     back into nature. Wood feels good in our hands with its warmth and distinct surface. Wood has a warm and vivid sound.

Product Details: 

🌈 Product dimensions: 19cm/7.5 in height x 39cm/15.3 in width x 7cm/2.8 in

🌈 To enhance the vibrant expression of wood, we only treat our wood with color and oil.

🌈 Recommended for children 2 years old and up.

🌈 These toys are hand crafted and machine made - not fully handmade.

🌈 Montessori is child-centered education designed to help all children reach their fullest potential – at their own pace. Its real-world approach 
      inspires a love of learning and readies students to study, work and live successfully in the 21st century.

🌈 Waldorf education is based on a thorough knowledge of the inner life of the child and follows his developmental stages. First, the child is  
      brought to experience things actively and then to feel these things, before finally approaching them intellectually.

🌈 Brain Power: Learning by Playing. Such instructive Montessori toys are particularly tailored for ages 2 and up, to make a grab and nurture head- 
      hand-eye coordination. Boost kids' creativity, and unlock the doors of imagination. Ideal indoor learning activities for kids ages 2-7, as it really 
      provides hours-long focus and fun!

🌈 Regretless Gift: Arched stacking block toys promote parent-children interaction. Based on the Waldorf concept, our toy, with high durability, is a 
      perfect companion for children’s growth. Natural wooden grain arouses children’s interest in nature, truly away from the quality-insecure 
      wooden toys, while no longer addicted to electronic devices.

🌈 Room Decor: Rainbow building blocks consist of 12 rainbow-coloured arches, every of which fits correctly together, thereby easy to balance like 
      a typical rainbow and make a design with. Vibrant colours and multi-use make up the DIY room decor for teen girls - boys, Montessori 
     classroom creations & more.

Benefits for Kids: 

🌈 Our toys are not just games in general, our toys can also train your child's brain performance if played regularly, so you can maximize your free 
      time to play together and train your child's abilities.

🌈 Provide a safe, engaging and nurturing environment for the child.

🌈 Promote trust in themselves and their world.

🌈 Develop gross motor coordination, fine motor skills, and language skill.

🌈 Offer opportunities to gain independence in daily tasks.

🌈 Contain a large variety of materials for the refinement of sensory perception and the development of literacy and mathematical understanding.

🌈 Offer opportunities for imaginative exploration leading to confident, creative self-expression.

Named Board With Animals, Personalized Christmas Gifts For Kids, Baby Nursery Decor, Best Birthday Boy Gift, Educational Puzzle
Description:
Personalized Name Puzzle With Animals from BusyPuzzle is the Best Wooden Gift for Kids

· COUPON ·
When buying 2 or more Baby Toys or Christmas Decor, we have an additional coupon discount: BUSYPUZZLE
Just add it to your shopping cart.

Our puzzle is based on all that you need. It will let you spend time with your child, will help him to develop his motor skills. Besides, we added an option to engrave Your unique message for your child. You both will enjoy it!

Baby is exploring the world with this game! He learns about what wood looks like and smells like, you can also show him colors. Of course, the baby will easily remember his name because children adore games, it is the best way to teach them. Furthermore, there are animals, so you can tell your baby about them, where do they live, what do they eat, etc. It is so important for the baby to learn the world around him, to know what the dog or cat is saying. And it will be more joyful if you will do it together!

It is the best way to show him how much you love him because for children it is important to be and play with their mom.

· Facilities Of Puzzles ·

- baby's own name
- different animals
- colors
- materials
- shapes and details

All these things your child can learn from just one Puzzle game! Show your baby how much you love him, present him with a special lovely puzzle.

· About Our Puzzles ·

It is made from wood and water-ink, so it is completely eco-friendly and safe for children and the environment.
It is easy to use and the perfect details’ size lets your baby take it comfy. We chose optimal width and this size got the highest mark from you. It perfectly fits your baby (we highly recommend it for 1+ babies).
Our puzzle was inspired by the Montessori technique. The simple technique of making a puzzle will let you do your own stuff while your baby is playing. But don't forget that you can spend time together and have fun.

· Actual Dimensions ·

PLEASE NOTE, that the size of board and animals was changed in order to keep same price.

Height:
4 animals: 5.9 inches (15.5 cm)
8 animals: 9 inches (23 cm)
*The length of the board depends of number of letters.

· Customization ·

Only in this puzzle, you can choose between 5 options (please, choose all the animals from the photo in the listing)
- name puzzle
- name puzzle with 1 animal
- name puzzle with 2 animals
- name with 4 animals
- name with 8 animals
You can also choose the base color (see infographic).

· You can choose one of the animal sets presented in the infographics. Also create your own puzzle by choosing the color of the name and variations of the animals.
· Choose the base of the puzzle. White base can be added at additional cost.
· You can add a unique engravement if you want.
· Gift Wrap is also important so we added options for you to choose from so you can order a real gift, not just a puzzle.
· And finally, we offer a puzzle stand so you can admire it every day.


· Have Any Questions ? ·

• If you got a damaged product - contact us. We are ready to return your full price for bad quality.
• Remember, that we don’t own delivery services and can’t control this process. So, if you have trouble with the time of shipping - check if your product was sent correctly. If all were sent in time - the problem is from the part of the delivery service.
• If your dog ate the shape of the puzzle or you lost it - we are ready to send you a new set of letters for a good price.


· Terms And Conditions For Safe Use ·

1. All kids have imagination. And we made all we can to give you a safe toy. But be careful and try not to leave your child alone with puzzles. Instead - play with your kid. Collect memories
2. Ensure that the child does not take small parts for him.
3. IF IN YOUR PUZZLE YOU HAVE LETTER ”I” - BE ATTENTIVE. THIS SHAPES CAN BE DANGEROUS FOR KIDS 0-3. DON’T LEAVE YOUR CHILD ALONE. OR WE CAN MAKE SHAPES BE FIXED TO THE PUZZLE.

Description:
Puzzle - Wood - Personalized - Children's room - Decoration - Design - Names - Wooden toys for toddlers - Gift - Birthday -
Montessori

The most unique wooden toy for the little ones.

If you are looking for a great gift for a baby or a super decoration for the nursery, then you have come to the right place.
A beautiful personalized wooden puzzle for your loved ones which promotes the motor skills of your baby and also serves as a decoration.

A great gift idea for the birthday, Christmas, baby shower and and and

Engraving: (1 letter extra to the name Order please.)
On the back of the puzzle an engraving can be ordered, on the photo are some examples. You can also write your own text in the personalization (max. 2 lines).


Practitioners:
The display with the engraving of the name, please order separately in the shop.

Material : - Spearwood 6 mm & 4 mm
The inlet of the letters is 4 mm deep.
The letters themselves are 6 mm thick and about 8 cm high
On request, the letters can be covered with a ball (pin).
Which makes it easier for the child to take out or insert the letters.

Poplar plywood is a natural raw material. Therefore, different grains, color differences after painting and also fine cracks are of course conditioned and not a reason for complaint.
It can also happen that a part of a layer breaks out through the different layers. This is not a reason for complaint.
Painting can lead to different shades of color.


Important******Important*******Important*******Important*******Important*******Important*******Important****** Important
Please check again before placing the order if everything is correct.
Please also check if you have received an email from us after the order, we will send it if something is wrong with the order or we still have questions about your wishes.

The puzzles are not toys but serve as decoration for the children's room.
The playful use is at your own guarantee.


The puzzles are painted with certified non-toxic paint that is safe for children.
The dried paint is suitable for children's toys according to DIN EN 71.3.

Made in Germany

Description:
The wooden name puzzle is a fun and effective way to teach your kids letters, colors, shapes, and…their unique names! Puzzle with pegs will save the day for parents looking to both entertain and teach the little ones. Made of non-toxic and durable materials, these Montessori toys are safe for little delicate hands. Besides, we produce each puzzle with smooth edges to ensure our little clients won't get hurt.

We've got loads of styles of baby toys that turn the process of learning letters into a play! Moms and dads are sure to order an item with their child's name on it crafted in eye-friendly colors. Whether you're looking for a personalized gift for the kid's 1st birthday or any other occasion, our portable products are absolutely recommended. 

Please, notice that if you don't mention design in your notes to order - you will get the design is shown on the main photo.  

Order our name puzzles to rock any special occasion!
★Perfect birthday gift for boys and girls to provide quality playtime.
★Cute present for Baby Shower party to make mom's job easier.
★Put our name puzzle under a Christmas tree and admire the little ones opening their presents in an excited mood!
★Order name puzzles to use them as cute nursery decor.
★Our wooden name puzzles are a perfect option to encourage independent play – all ages have fun manipulating each piece, taking it out, testing its durability, and putting it back. If necessary, you’re welcome to join the little one and do the puzzle together!

Details:
★Made out of non-toxic and durable birch plywood.
★Organic and safe materials and paints are used in the production process.
★The shapes on the sides are included in the price.
★GIFT packaging is available at checkout.
★Each name puzzle is a personalized eco-friendly product.
★Each puzzle is 0.31 inches thin (8mm) and each letter is 0.15 inches thin (4mm) and 2.36 inches tall (6cm).

It takes 1-3 business days to craft a wooden name puzzle. Looking for a custom design? We’ll be happy to meet your requirements, but we will need a bit more time to do the job.

Canada - 3-6 business days. 
Standard delivery to the other counties - 3-6 business days.

Description:
Personalized Puzzle Name Board, Toy Gifts for Baby Girls, Custom Name Puzzle for Toddlers, Custom Wooden Baby Keepsake, Baby Shower Gift

Our custom puzzle board is both durable and environmentally friendly. The busy board is not only a toy for entertainment but also a montessori toy for children's fundamental development, such as identity colors, shapes, animal species, spelling their names, etc. The wooden puzzle board is the perfect gift for children aged 1 to 10 who are always hungry to learn. It can be a birthday present, a holiday gift for your kids and your friend's kids, or even a memorial keepsake as well. Our wooden name puzzle encourages children to play independently and they can have fun with each piece of the puzzle. 

🚀 Personalize: The puzzle will be customized with a name, and colors, with your message engraved on the back of the board.
🚀 Dimensions: 38 x 30 cm, or 15" x 11.8 " (It depends on the length of your child's name, and the number of elements shown on the board)
🚀 Weight: 200 - 500 (grams) (It depends on the length of your child's name, and the number of elements shown on the board)
🚀 Material:  Natural birch plywood and water-based ink

Usage and storage

All of the letters and elements on the board have been researched and measured to ensure their safety.
Children, on the other hand, should be aware of the letter "I," which may be a little easy to swallow, and parents should play with them.
Clean the puzzle with a damp paper or towel and leave it to dry naturally; do not wash or rinse with water.

Description:
Our personalized name puzzles make the perfect gift for first birthday's, baby showers, Easter, or any occasion!

A gift you love giving, our wooden name puzzles are a wonderful learning toy to give for birthdays, special occasions and "Just because I Love You"!

• FREE Shipping!
• Personalized gift shows you care
• Fun and educational
• Stand available separately, see link below
• Handmade in Upstate, NY

COLORS: This puzzle includes Olive Green, Light Sage Green, and Ochre Yellow

Puzzles are a fun learning toy that encourage name recognition, spelling, and fine motor skills. They are time tested and never go out of style. Made of high quality baltic birch, our puzzles are 4.5" tall and the length varies based on the length of the name. The puzzles typically range from 10" long, to a maximum length of 23" based on the number of letters and shapes. The letters are approximately 3" high, the perfect size to grab for your young learner. All of the puzzle pieces are raised, making it easy to get them out and play with. We use a combination of non-toxic paint, eco friendly ink, and a food grade non-toxic wood sealer that is child friendly on our puzzles.

The exact colors used and order of the colors will vary from puzzle to puzzle. The number of colors used varies based on the number of letters in a name. Due to differences in monitors and devices, the colors may appear slightly different than shown on your screen. If you have a specific request, please leave it in the Notes to Seller and we are happy to accommodate you if we can. We are not able to include special characters like hyphens or apostrophes in our puzzles. Our puzzles only include uppercase letters, without any special characters.

SENDING AS A GIFT: We offer gift wrap, and can enclose a gift message for you. Please choose the gift wrap or gift note selections at checkout. We do not send a packing slip with price on any of our orders, as many orders are sent directly to the recipient as a gift.

PUZZLE STAND:
To add a puzzle display stand, please use this listing. You can add both items to your cart and checkout at once to receive free shipping on the stand!
https://www.etsy.com/listing/815194794

FREE SHIPPING: We offer FREE 2 Day Shipping on most orders via UPS 3 Day Air. In select locations that we are unable to ship UPS, such as PO Boxes, Hawaii, and Alaska, as well as rural locations without UPS delivery, we ship via USPS Priority Mail.

RETURNS: We do not accept returns on customized items. However, if you have any questions or concerns with your order, please don't hesitate to reach out. Our number one goal is that you LOVE your order! If we make a mistake, we will always make it right for you.

CANCELLATIONS: We work hard to start work on your order as soon as possible! Due to our quick processing time and the personalized nature of this product, we are currently unable to accept cancellations after the order is placed. If you have any questions, please feel free to reach out before placing your order. Thank you!
